164constexpr auto createObservedDomain = "CREATE TABLE ObservedDomains ("
165 "domainID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, registrableDomain TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE ON CONFLICT FAIL, lastSeen REAL NOT NULL, "
166 "hadUserInteraction INTEGER NOT NULL, mostRecentUserInteractionTime REAL NOT NULL, grandfathered INTEGER NOT NULL, "
167 "isPrevalent INTEGER NOT NULL, isVeryPrevalent INTEGER NOT NULL, dataRecordsRemoved INTEGER NOT NULL,"
168 "timesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToUserInteraction INTEGER NOT NULL, timesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPI INTEGER NOT NULL,"
169 "isScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval INTEGER NOT NULL)"_s;
170
171enum {
172 DomainIDIndex,
173 RegistrableDomainIndex,
174 LastSeenIndex,
175 HadUserInteractionIndex,
176 MostRecentUserInteractionTimeIndex,
177 GrandfatheredIndex,
178 IsPrevalentIndex,
179 IsVeryPrevalentIndex,
180 DataRecordsRemovedIndex,
181 TimesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToUserInteractionIndex,
182 TimesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPIIndex,
183 IsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemovalIndex
184};

187 "topLevelDomainID INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, CONSTRAINT fkDomainID FOREIGN KEY(topLevelDomainID) "
188 "REFERENCES ObservedDomains(domainID) ON DELETE CASCADE)"_s;

190constexpr auto createStorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains = "CREATE TABLE StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains ("
191 "domainID INTEGER NOT NULL, topLevelDomainID INTEGER NOT NULL ON CONFLICT FAIL, "
192 "CONSTRAINT fkDomainID FOREIGN KEY(domainID) REFERENCES ObservedDomains(domainID) ON DELETE CASCADE, "
193 "FOREIGN KEY(topLevelDomainID) REFERENCES ObservedDomains(domainID) ON DELETE CASCADE)"_s;

296static bool needsNewCreateTableSchema(const String& schema)
297{
298 return schema.contains("REFERENCES TopLevelDomains");
299}
300
301static String stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(const char* originalQuery)
302{
303 return String(originalQuery).replace("CREATE UNIQUE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS", "CREATE UNIQUE INDEX");
304}
305
306static const MemoryCompactLookupOnlyRobinHoodHashMap<String, TableAndIndexPair>& expectedTableAndIndexQueries()
307{
308 static auto expectedTableAndIndexQueries = makeNeverDestroyed(MemoryCompactLookupOnlyRobinHoodHashMap<String, TableAndIndexPair> {
309 { "ObservedDomains"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createObservedDomain, std::nullopt) },
310 { "TopLevelDomains"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createTopLevelDomains, std::nullopt) },
311 { "StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createStorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexStorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains)) },
312 { "TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createTopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexTopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo)) },
313 { "TopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createTopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexTopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement)) },
314 { "TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createTopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexTopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom)) },
315 { "TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createTopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexTopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom)) },
316 { "TopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createTopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexTopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts)) },
317 { "SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createSubframeUnderTopFrameDomains, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexSubframeUnderTopFrameDomains)) },
318 { "SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createSubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains)) },
319 { "SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createSubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo)) },
320 { "SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createSubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom)) },
321 { "OperatingDates"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createOperatingDates, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexOperatingDates)) },
322 { "UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createUnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexUnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement)) },
323 { "AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s, std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(createAttributedPrivateClickMeasurement, stripIndexQueryToMatchStoredValue(createUniqueIndexAttributedPrivateClickMeasurement)) }
324 });
325
326 return expectedTableAndIndexQueries;
327}

337ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore(WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore& store, WorkQueue& workQueue, ShouldIncludeLocalhost shouldIncludeLocalhost, const String& storageDirectoryPath, PAL::SessionID sessionID)
338 : ResourceLoadStatisticsStore(store, workQueue, shouldIncludeLocalhost)
339 , m_storageDirectoryPath(FileSystem::pathByAppendingComponent(storageDirectoryPath, "observations.db"_s))
340 , m_sessionID(sessionID)
341{
342 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
343
344 openAndUpdateSchemaIfNecessary();
345 enableForeignKeys();
346
347 // Since we are using a workerQueue, the sequential dispatch blocks may be called by different threads.
348 m_database.disableThreadingChecks();
349
350 if (!m_database.turnOnIncrementalAutoVacuum())
351 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::turnOnIncrementalAutoVacuum failed, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
352
353 includeTodayAsOperatingDateIfNecessary();
354 allStores().add(this);
355}

357ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::~ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore()
358{
359 close();
360 allStores().remove(this);
361}

366 if (m_database.isOpen())
367 m_database.close();
368}

370void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::openITPDatabase()
371{
372 if (!FileSystem::fileExists(m_storageDirectoryPath)) {
373 if (!FileSystem::makeAllDirectories(FileSystem::parentPath(m_storageDirectoryPath))) {
374 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::open failed, error message: Failed to create directory database path: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_storageDirectoryPath.utf8().data());
375 return;
376 }
377 m_isNewResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseFile = true;
378 } else
379 m_isNewResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseFile = false;
380
381 if (!m_database.open(m_storageDirectoryPath)) {
382 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::open failed, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING ", database path: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg(), m_storageDirectoryPath.utf8().data());
383 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
384 }
385
386 auto setBusyTimeout = m_database.prepareStatement("PRAGMA busy_timeout = 5000"_s);
387 if (!setBusyTimeout || setBusyTimeout->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
388 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::setBusyTimeout failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
389 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
390 return;
391 }
392
393 if (m_isNewResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseFile) {
394 if (!createSchema()) {
395 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::createSchema failed, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING ", database path: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg(), m_storageDirectoryPath.utf8().data());
396 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
397 return;
398 }
399 }
400}

402std::optional<Vector<String>> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::checkForMissingTablesInSchema()
403{
404 Vector<String> missingTables;
405 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT 1 from sqlite_master WHERE type='table' and tbl_name=?"_s);
406 if (!statement) {
407 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::checkForMissingTablesInSchema failed to prepare, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
408 return std::nullopt;
409 }
410
411 for (auto& table : expectedTableAndIndexQueries().keys()) {
412 if (statement->bindText(1, table) != SQLITE_OK) {
413 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::checkForMissingTablesInSchema failed to bind, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
414 return std::nullopt;
415 }
416 if (statement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
417 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::checkForMissingTablesInSchema schema is missing table: %s", this, table.ascii().data());
418 missingTables.append(String(table));
419 }
420 statement->reset();
421 }
422 if (missingTables.isEmpty())
423 return std::nullopt;
424
425 return missingTables;
426}

428void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::enableForeignKeys()
429{
430 auto enableForeignKeys = m_database.prepareStatement("PRAGMA foreign_keys = ON"_s);
431 if (!enableForeignKeys || enableForeignKeys->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
432 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::enableForeignKeys failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
433 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
434 return;
435 }
436}
437
438TableAndIndexPair ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::currentTableAndIndexQueries(const String& tableName)
439{
440 auto getTableStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT sql FROM sqlite_master WHERE tbl_name=? AND type = 'table'"_s);
441 if (!getTableStatement) {
442 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::currentTableAndIndexQueries Unable to prepare statement to fetch schema for the table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
443 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
444 return { };
445 }
446
447 if (getTableStatement->bindText(1, tableName) != SQLITE_OK) {
448 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::currentTableAndIndexQueries Unable to bind statement to fetch schema for the table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
449 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
450 return { };
451 }
452
453 if (getTableStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
454 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::currentTableAndIndexQueries error executing statement to fetch table schema, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
455 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
456 return { };
457 }
458
459 String createTableQuery = getTableStatement->columnText(0);
460
461 auto getIndexStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT sql FROM sqlite_master WHERE tbl_name=? AND type = 'index'"_s);
462 if (!getIndexStatement) {
463 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::currentTableAndIndexQueries Unable to prepare statement to fetch index for the table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
464 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
465 return { };
466 }
467
468 if (getIndexStatement->bindText(1, tableName) != SQLITE_OK) {
469 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::currentTableAndIndexQueries Unable to bind statement to fetch index for the table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
470 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
471 return { };
472 }
473
474 std::optional<String> index;
475 if (getIndexStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
476 auto rawIndex = String(getIndexStatement->columnText(0));
477 if (!rawIndex.isEmpty())
478 index = rawIndex;
479 }
480
481 return std::make_pair<String, std::optional<String>>(WTFMove(createTableQuery), WTFMove(index));
482}
483
484bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::needsUpdatedPrivateClickMeasurementSchema()
485{
486 auto currentSchema = currentTableAndIndexQueries("AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s).first;
487
488 if (!currentSchema.isEmpty() && currentSchema != createAttributedPrivateClickMeasurement)
489 return true;
490
491 return false;
492}

494bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::missingUniqueIndices()
495{
496 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM sqlite_master WHERE type = 'index'"_s);
497 if (!statement) {
498 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::missingUniqueIndices Unable to prepare statement to fetch index count, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
499 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
500 return { };
501 }
502
503 if (statement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
504 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::missingUniqueIndices error executing statement to fetch index count, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
505 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
506 return { };
507 }
508
509 if (statement->columnInt(0) < expectedIndexCount)
510 return true;
511
512 return false;
513}
514
515bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::missingReferenceToObservedDomains()
516{
517 // Check a table for a reference to TopLevelDomains, a sign of the old schema.
518 auto oldSchema = currentTableAndIndexQueries("TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo"_s).first;
519 return needsNewCreateTableSchema(oldSchema);
520}
521
522bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::needsUpdatedSchema()
523{
524 // There are 3 cases where we expect potential schema changes due to upgrades.
525 // All other tables should be up-to-date, so we should ASSERT that they are correct.
526 if (missingReferenceToObservedDomains() || needsUpdatedPrivateClickMeasurementSchema() || missingUniqueIndices())
527 return true;
528
529 for (auto& table : expectedTableAndIndexQueries().keys()) {
530 UNUSED_PARAM(table);
531 ASSERT(currentTableAndIndexQueries(table) == expectedTableAndIndexQueries().get(table));
532 }
533
534 return false;
535}
536
537static Expected<SQLiteStatement, int> insertDistinctValuesInTableStatement(SQLiteDatabase& database, const String& table)
538{
539 if (table == "SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains")
540 return database.prepareStatement("INSERT INTO SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains SELECT subFrameDomainID, MAX(lastUpdated), topFrameDomainID FROM _SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains GROUP BY subFrameDomainID, topFrameDomainID"_s);
541
542 if (table == "SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains")
543 return database.prepareStatement("INSERT INTO SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains SELECT subresourceDomainID, MAX(lastUpdated), topFrameDomainID FROM _SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains GROUP BY subresourceDomainID, topFrameDomainID"_s);
544
545 if (table == "SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo")
546 return database.prepareStatement("INSERT INTO SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo SELECT subresourceDomainID, MAX(lastUpdated), toDomainID FROM _SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo GROUP BY subresourceDomainID, toDomainID"_s);
547
548 if (table == "TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom")
549 return database.prepareStatement("INSERT INTO TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom SELECT toDomainID, MAX(lastUpdated), fromDomainID FROM _TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom GROUP BY toDomainID, fromDomainID"_s);
550
551 if (table == "UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement")
552 return database.prepareStatement("INSERT INTO UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement SELECT sourceSiteDomainID, destinationSiteDomainID, sourceID, MAX(timeOfAdClick), token, signature, keyID FROM _UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement GROUP BY sourceSiteDomainID, destinationSiteDomainID"_s);
553
554 if (table == "AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement")
555 return database.prepareStatement("INSERT INTO AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement SELECT sourceSiteDomainID, destinationSiteDomainID, sourceID, attributionTriggerData, priority, MAX(timeOfAdClick), earliestTimeToSendToSource, token, signature, keyID, earliestTimeToSendToDestination FROM _AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement GROUP BY sourceSiteDomainID, destinationSiteDomainID"_s);
556
557 return database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("INSERT INTO ", table, " SELECT DISTINCT * FROM _", table));
558}
559
560void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary()
561{
562 if (!needsUpdatedSchema())
563 return;
564
565 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
566 transaction.begin();
567
568 for (auto& table : expectedTableAndIndexQueries().keys()) {
569 auto alterTable = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("ALTER TABLE ", table, " RENAME TO _", table));
570 if (!alterTable || alterTable->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
571 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary failed to rename table, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
572 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
573 return;
574 }
575 }
576
577 if (!createSchema()) {
578 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary failed to create schema, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
579 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
580 return;
581 }
582
583 for (auto& table : expectedTableAndIndexQueries().keys()) {
584 auto migrateTableData = insertDistinctValuesInTableStatement(m_database, table);
585 if (!migrateTableData || migrateTableData->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
586 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary failed to migrate schema, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
587 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
588 return;
589 }
590
591 auto dropTableQuery = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("DROP TABLE _", table));
592 if (!dropTableQuery || dropTableQuery->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
593 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary failed to drop temporary tables, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
594 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
595 return;
596 }
597 }
598
599 transaction.commit();
600
601 if (!createUniqueIndices()) {
602 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary failed to create unique indices, error message: %s", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
603 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
604 return;
605 }
606}
607
608Vector<String> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::columnsForTable(const String& tableName)
609{
610 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("PRAGMA table_info(", tableName, ")"));
611
612 if (!statement) {
613 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::getColumnsFromTableInfoStatement Unable to prepare statement to fetch schema for table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
614 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
615 return { };
616 }
617
618 Vector<String> columns;
619 while (statement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
620 auto name = statement->columnText(1);
621 columns.append(name);
622 }
623
624 return columns;
625}
626
627void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingColumnsToTable(String&& tableName, const ExistingColumns& existingColumns, const ExpectedColumns& expectedColumns)
628{
629 ASSERT(existingColumns.size() <= expectedColumns.size());
630
631 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
632 for (auto& column : expectedColumns) {
633 if (existingColumns.contains(column))
634 continue;
635
636 if (!transaction.inProgress())
637 transaction.begin();
638
639 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("ALTER TABLE ", tableName, " ADD COLUMN ", column));
640 if (!statement) {
641 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingColumnsToTable Unable to prepare statement to add missing columns to table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
642 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
643 return;
644 }
645 if (statement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
646 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingColumnsToTable error executing statement to add missing columns to table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
647 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
648 return;
649 }
650 statement->reset();
651 }
652 transaction.commit();
653}
654
655void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingColumnsIfNecessary()
656{
657 const auto unattributedTableName = "UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s;
658 const auto attributedTableName = "AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s;
659
660 addMissingColumnsToTable(unattributedTableName, columnsForTable(unattributedTableName), expectedUnattributedColumns());
661 addMissingColumnsToTable(attributedTableName, columnsForTable(attributedTableName), expectedAttributedColumns());
662}

664void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::renameColumnInTable(String&& tableName, ExistingColumnName&& existingColumnName, ExpectedColumnName&& expectedColumnName)
665{
666 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("ALTER TABLE ", tableName, " RENAME COLUMN ", existingColumnName, " TO ", expectedColumnName));
667 if (!statement) {
668 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingColumnsToTable Unable to prepare statement to rename column in table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
669 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
670 return;
671 }
672 if (statement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
673 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingColumnsToTable error executing statement to rename column in table, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
674 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
675 return;
676 }
677}
678
679void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::renameColumnsIfNecessary()
680{
681 // Attributed Private Click Measurement case.
682 const auto attributedTableName = "AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s;
683 const auto oldEarliestTimeToSendColumn = "earliestTimeToSend"_s;
684 const auto newEarliestTimeToSendColumn = "earliestTimeToSendToSource"_s;
685 const auto oldAttributionDestinationColumn = "attributeOnSiteDomainID"_s;
686 const auto newAttributionDestinationColumn = "destinationSiteDomainID"_s;
687 const auto foundAttributedTableColumns = columnsForTable(attributedTableName);
688
689 if (foundAttributedTableColumns.contains(oldEarliestTimeToSendColumn))
690 renameColumnInTable(attributedTableName, oldEarliestTimeToSendColumn, newEarliestTimeToSendColumn);
691
692 if (foundAttributedTableColumns.contains(oldAttributionDestinationColumn))
693 renameColumnInTable(attributedTableName, oldAttributionDestinationColumn, newAttributionDestinationColumn);
694
695 // Unattributed Private Click Measurement case.
696 auto unattributedTableName = "UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement"_s;
697 auto foundUnattributedTableColumns = columnsForTable(unattributedTableName);
698
699 if (foundUnattributedTableColumns.contains(oldAttributionDestinationColumn))
700 renameColumnInTable(unattributedTableName, oldAttributionDestinationColumn, newAttributionDestinationColumn);
701}
702
703void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingTablesIfNecessary()
704{
705 auto missingTables = checkForMissingTablesInSchema();
706 if (!missingTables)
707 return;
708
709 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
710 transaction.begin();
711 for (auto& table : *missingTables) {
712 auto createTableQuery = expectedTableAndIndexQueries().get(table).first;
713 if (!m_database.executeCommandSlow(createTableQuery))
714 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingTables failed to execute, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
715 }
716
717 if (!createUniqueIndices()) {
718 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::addMissingTables failed to create unique indices, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
719 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
720 return;
721 }
722 transaction.commit();
723}
724
725void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::openAndUpdateSchemaIfNecessary()
726{
727 openITPDatabase();
728 addMissingTablesIfNecessary();
729
730 String currentSchema;
731 {
732 // Fetch the schema for an existing Observed Domains table.
733 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT type, sql FROM sqlite_master WHERE tbl_name='ObservedDomains'"_s);
734 if (!statement) {
735 LOG_ERROR("Unable to prepare statement to fetch schema for the ObservedDomains table.");
736 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
737 return;
738 }
739
740 // If there is no ObservedDomains table at all, or there is an error executing the fetch, delete the file.
741 if (statement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
742 LOG_ERROR("Error executing statement to fetch schema for the Observed Domains table.");
743 close();
744 FileSystem::deleteFile(m_storageDirectoryPath);
745 openITPDatabase();
746 return;
747 }
748
749 currentSchema = statement->columnText(1);
750 }
751
752 ASSERT(!currentSchema.isEmpty());
753
754 // If the ObservedDomains schema in the ResourceLoadStatistics directory is not the current schema, delete the database file.
755 // FIXME: Migrate old ObservedDomains data to new table schema.
756 if (currentSchema != ObservedDomainsTableSchemaV1() && currentSchema != ObservedDomainsTableSchemaV1Alternate()) {
757 close();
758 FileSystem::deleteFile(m_storageDirectoryPath);
759 openITPDatabase();
760 return;
761 }
762
763 // Renaming and adding columns should be done before migrating to avoid mismatched or missing columns.
764 renameColumnsIfNecessary();
765 addMissingColumnsIfNecessary();
766 migrateDataToNewTablesIfNecessary();
767}
768
769SQLiteStatementAutoResetScope ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::scopedStatement(std::unique_ptr<WebCore::SQLiteStatement>& statement, ASCIILiteral query, const String& logString) const
770{
771 if (!statement) {
772 auto statementOrError = m_database.prepareHeapStatement(query);
773 if (!statementOrError) {
774 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::%s failed to prepare statement, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, logString.ascii().data(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
775 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
776 return SQLiteStatementAutoResetScope { };
777 }
778 statement = statementOrError.value().moveToUniquePtr();
779 ASSERT(m_database.isOpen());
780 }
781 return SQLiteStatementAutoResetScope { statement.get() };
782}
783
784void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::interrupt()
785{
786 if (m_database.isOpen())
787 m_database.interrupt();
788}
789
790bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::isEmpty() const
791{
792 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
793
794 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_observedDomainCountStatement, observedDomainCountQuery, "isEmpty"_s);
795 if (!scopedStatement
796 || scopedStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
797 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::isEmpty failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
798 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
799 return false;
800 }
801 return !scopedStatement->columnInt(0);
802}
803
804bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::createUniqueIndices()
805{
806 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexStorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains)
807 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexTopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo)
808 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexTopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement)
809 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexTopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom)
810 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexTopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom)
811 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexTopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts)
812 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexSubframeUnderTopFrameDomains)
813 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains)
814 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo)
815 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom)
816 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexSubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains)
817 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexOperatingDates)
818 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexUnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement)
819 || !m_database.executeCommand(createUniqueIndexAttributedPrivateClickMeasurement)) {
820 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::createUniqueIndices failed to execute, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
821 return false;
822 }
823 return true;
824}
825
826bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::createSchema()
827{
828 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
829
830 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createObservedDomain)) {
831 LOG_ERROR("Could not create ObservedDomains table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
832 return false;
833 }
834
835 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createTopLevelDomains)) {
836 LOG_ERROR("Could not create TopLevelDomains table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
837 return false;
838 }
839
840 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createStorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains)) {
841 LOG_ERROR("Could not create StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
842 return false;
843 }
844
845 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createTopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo)) {
846 LOG_ERROR("Could not create TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
847 return false;
848 }
849
850 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createTopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement)) {
851 LOG_ERROR("Could not create TopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
852 return false;
853 }
854
855 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createTopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom)) {
856 LOG_ERROR("Could not create TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
857 return false;
858 }
859
860 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createTopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom)) {
861 LOG_ERROR("Could not create TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
862 return false;
863 }
864
865 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createTopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts)) {
866 LOG_ERROR("Could not create TopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
867 return false;
868 }
869
870 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createSubframeUnderTopFrameDomains)) {
871 LOG_ERROR("Could not create SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
872 return false;
873 }
874
875 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createSubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains)) {
876 LOG_ERROR("Could not create SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
877 return false;
878 }
879
880 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createSubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo)) {
881 LOG_ERROR("Could not create SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
882 return false;
883 }
884
885 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createSubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom)) {
886 LOG_ERROR("Could not create SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
887 return false;
888 }
889
890 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createOperatingDates)) {
891 LOG_ERROR("Could not create OperatingDates table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
892 return false;
893 }
894
895 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createUnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement)) {
896 LOG_ERROR("Could not create UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
897 return false;
898 }
899
900 if (!m_database.executeCommand(createAttributedPrivateClickMeasurement)) {
901 LOG_ERROR("Could not create AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement table in database (%i) - %s", m_database.lastError(), m_database.lastErrorMsg());
902 return false;
903 }
904
905 if (!createUniqueIndices())
906 return false;
907
908 return true;
909}

969bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertObservedDomain(const ResourceLoadStatistics& loadStatistics)
970{
971 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
972
973 if (domainID(loadStatistics.registrableDomain)) {
974 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertObservedDomain can only be called on domains not in the database.");
975 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
976 return false;
977 }
978 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_insertObservedDomainStatement, insertObservedDomainQuery, "insertObservedDomain"_s);
979 if (!scopedStatement
980 || scopedStatement->bindText(RegistrableDomainIndex, loadStatistics.registrableDomain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
981 || scopedStatement->bindDouble(LastSeenIndex, loadStatistics.lastSeen.secondsSinceEpoch().value()) != SQLITE_OK
982 || scopedStatement->bindInt(HadUserInteractionIndex, loadStatistics.hadUserInteraction) != SQLITE_OK
983 || scopedStatement->bindDouble(MostRecentUserInteractionTimeIndex, loadStatistics.mostRecentUserInteractionTime.secondsSinceEpoch().value()) != SQLITE_OK
984 || scopedStatement->bindInt(GrandfatheredIndex, loadStatistics.grandfathered) != SQLITE_OK
985 || scopedStatement->bindInt(IsPrevalentIndex, loadStatistics.isPrevalentResource) != SQLITE_OK
986 || scopedStatement->bindInt(IsVeryPrevalentIndex, loadStatistics.isVeryPrevalentResource) != SQLITE_OK
987 || scopedStatement->bindInt(DataRecordsRemovedIndex, loadStatistics.dataRecordsRemoved) != SQLITE_OK
988 || scopedStatement->bindInt(TimesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToUserInteractionIndex, loadStatistics.timesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToUserInteraction) != SQLITE_OK
989 || scopedStatement->bindInt(TimesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPIIndex, loadStatistics.timesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPI) != SQLITE_OK
990 || scopedStatement->bindInt(IsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemovalIndex, loadStatistics.gotLinkDecorationFromPrevalentResource) != SQLITE_OK) {
991 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertObservedDomain failed to bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
992 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
993 return false;
994 }
995
996 if (scopedStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
997 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertObservedDomain failed to commit, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
998 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
999 return false;
1000 }
1001 return true;
1002}
1003
1004bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::relationshipExists(SQLiteStatementAutoResetScope& statement, std::optional<unsigned> firstDomainID, const RegistrableDomain& secondDomain) const
1005{
1006 if (!firstDomainID)
1007 return false;
1008
1009 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1010
1011 if (!statement
1012 || statement->bindInt(1, *firstDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
1013 || statement->bindText(2, secondDomain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
1014 || statement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
1015 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::relationshipExists failed to bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1016 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1017 return false;
1018 }
1019 return !!statement->columnInt(0);
1020}

1022std::optional<unsigned> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::domainID(const RegistrableDomain& domain) const
1023{
1024 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1025
1026 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_domainIDFromStringStatement, domainIDFromStringQuery, "domainID"_s);
1027 if (!scopedStatement || scopedStatement->bindText(1, domain.string()) != SQLITE_OK) {
1028 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::domainIDFromString failed. Error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1029 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1030 return std::nullopt;
1031 }
1032
1033 if (scopedStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW)
1034 return std::nullopt;
1035
1036 return scopedStatement->columnInt(0);
1037}

1039String ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensureAndMakeDomainList(const SQLiteTransaction&, const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domainList)
1040{
1041 ASSERT(m_database.transactionInProgress());
1042
1043 StringBuilder builder;
1044 for (auto& topFrameResource : domainList) {
1045 // Insert query will fail if top frame domain is not already in the database
1046 if (ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(topFrameResource).second)
1047 builder.append(builder.isEmpty() ? "" : ", ", '"', topFrameResource.string(), '"');
1048 }
1049 return builder.toString();
1050}
1051
1052void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertDomainRelationshipList(const SQLiteTransaction& transaction, const String& statement, const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domainList, unsigned domainID)
1053{
1054 auto insertRelationshipStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString(statement, ensureAndMakeDomainList(transaction, domainList), " );"));
1055
1056 if (!insertRelationshipStatement
1057 || insertRelationshipStatement->bindInt(1, domainID) != SQLITE_OK) {
1058 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertDomainRelationshipList failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1059 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1060 return;
1061 }
1062
1063 if (statement.contains("REPLACE")) {
1064 if (insertRelationshipStatement->bindDouble(2, WallTime::now().secondsSinceEpoch().value()) != SQLITE_OK) {
1065 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertDomainRelationshipList failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1066 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1067 return;
1068 }
1069 }
1070
1071 if (insertRelationshipStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1072 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertDomainRelationshipList failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1073 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1074 return;
1075 }
1076}
1077
1078void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertDomainRelationships(const SQLiteTransaction& transaction, const ResourceLoadStatistics& loadStatistics)
1079{
1080 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1081 ASSERT(m_database.transactionInProgress());
1082
1083 auto registrableDomainID = domainID(loadStatistics.registrableDomain);
1084
1085 if (!registrableDomainID)
1086 return;
1087
1088 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, storageAccessUnderTopFrameDomainsQuery, loadStatistics.storageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains, registrableDomainID.value());
1089 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameUniqueRedirectsToQuery, loadStatistics.topFrameUniqueRedirectsTo, registrableDomainID.value());
1090 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcementQuery, loadStatistics.topFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement, registrableDomainID.value());
1091 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameUniqueRedirectsFromQuery, loadStatistics.topFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom, registrableDomainID.value());
1092 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsQuery, loadStatistics.subframeUnderTopFrameDomains, registrableDomainID.value());
1093 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsQuery, loadStatistics.subresourceUnderTopFrameDomains, registrableDomainID.value());
1094 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subresourceUniqueRedirectsToQuery, loadStatistics.subresourceUniqueRedirectsTo, registrableDomainID.value());
1095 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subresourceUniqueRedirectsFromQuery, loadStatistics.subresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom, registrableDomainID.value());
1096 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameLinkDecorationsFromQuery, loadStatistics.topFrameLinkDecorationsFrom, registrableDomainID.value());
1097 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameLoadedThirdPartyScriptsQuery, loadStatistics.topFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts, registrableDomainID.value());
1098}
1099
1100void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::populateFromMemoryStore(const ResourceLoadStatisticsMemoryStore& memoryStore)
1101{
1102 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1103
1104 if (!isEmpty())
1105 return;
1106
1107 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1108 transaction.begin();
1109
1110 auto& statisticsMap = memoryStore.data();
1111 for (const auto& statistic : statisticsMap.values()) {
1112 auto result = insertObservedDomain(statistic);
1113 if (!result) {
1114 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::populateFromMemoryStore insertObservedDomain failed to complete, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1115 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1116 return;
1117 }
1118 }
1119
1120 // Make a separate pass for inter-domain relationships so we
1121 // can refer to the ObservedDomain table entries
1122 for (auto& statistic : statisticsMap.values())
1123 insertDomainRelationships(transaction, statistic);
1124
1125 transaction.commit();
1126}
1127
1128void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::merge(const SQLiteTransaction& transaction, WebCore::SQLiteStatement* current, const ResourceLoadStatistics& other)
1129{
1130 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1131 ASSERT(m_database.transactionInProgress());
1132
1133 auto currentRegistrableDomain = current->columnText(RegistrableDomainIndex);
1134 auto currentLastSeen = current->columnDouble(LastSeenIndex);
1135 auto currentMostRecentUserInteraction = current->columnDouble(MostRecentUserInteractionTimeIndex);
1136 bool currentGrandfathered = current->columnInt(GrandfatheredIndex);
1137 bool currentIsPrevalent = current->columnInt(IsPrevalentIndex);
1138 bool currentIsVeryPrevalent = current->columnInt(IsVeryPrevalentIndex);
1139 unsigned currentDataRecordsRemoved = current->columnInt(DataRecordsRemovedIndex);
1140 bool currentIsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval = current->columnInt(IsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemovalIndex);
1141
1142 ASSERT(currentRegistrableDomain == other.registrableDomain.string());
1143
1144 if (WallTime::fromRawSeconds(currentLastSeen) < other.lastSeen)
1145 updateLastSeen(other.registrableDomain, other.lastSeen);
1146
1147 if (!other.hadUserInteraction) {
1148 // If most recent user interaction time has been reset do so here too.
1149 if (!other.mostRecentUserInteractionTime)
1150 setUserInteraction(other.registrableDomain, false, { });
1151 } else
1152 setUserInteraction(other.registrableDomain, true, std::max(WallTime::fromRawSeconds(currentMostRecentUserInteraction), other.mostRecentUserInteractionTime));
1153
1154 if (other.grandfathered && !currentGrandfathered)
1155 setGrandfathered(transaction, other.registrableDomain, true);
1156 if (other.isPrevalentResource && !currentIsPrevalent)
1157 setPrevalentResource(transaction, other.registrableDomain);
1158 if (other.isVeryPrevalentResource && !currentIsVeryPrevalent)
1159 setVeryPrevalentResource(transaction, other.registrableDomain);
1160 if (other.dataRecordsRemoved > currentDataRecordsRemoved)
1161 updateDataRecordsRemoved(other.registrableDomain, other.dataRecordsRemoved);
1162 if (other.gotLinkDecorationFromPrevalentResource && !currentIsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval)
1163 setIsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval(transaction, other.registrableDomain, true);
1164}
1165
1166void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::mergeStatistic(const SQLiteTransaction& transaction, const ResourceLoadStatistics& statistic)
1167{
1168 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1169
1170 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_getResourceDataByDomainNameStatement, getResourceDataByDomainNameQuery, "mergeStatistic"_s);
1171 if (!scopedStatement
1172 || scopedStatement->bindText(1, statistic.registrableDomain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
1173 || scopedStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
1174 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::mergeStatistic. Statement failed to bind or domain was not found, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1175 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1176 return;
1177 }
1178
1179 merge(transaction, scopedStatement.get(), statistic);
1180}
1181
1182void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::mergeStatistics(Vector<ResourceLoadStatistics>&& statistics)
1183{
1184 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1185 if (statistics.isEmpty())
1186 return;
1187
1188 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1189 transaction.begin();
1190
1191 for (auto& statistic : statistics) {
1192 if (!domainID(statistic.registrableDomain)) {
1193 auto result = insertObservedDomain(statistic);
1194 if (!result) {
1195 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::mergeStatistics insertObservedDomain failed to complete, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1196 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1197 return;
1198 }
1199 } else
1200 mergeStatistic(transaction, statistic);
1201 }
1202
1203 // Make a separate pass for inter-domain relationships so we
1204 // can refer to the ObservedDomain table entries.
1205 for (auto& statistic : statistics)
1206 insertDomainRelationships(transaction, statistic);
1207
1208 transaction.commit();
1209}
1210
1211static ASCIILiteral joinSubStatisticsForSorting()
1212{
1213 return "SELECT domainID,"
1214 "(countSubFrameUnderTopFrame + countSubResourceUnderTopFrame + countUniqueRedirectTo) as sum "
1215 "FROM ( "
1216 "SELECT "
1217 "domainID, "
1218 "COUNT(DISTINCT f.topFrameDomainID) as countSubFrameUnderTopFrame, "
1219 "COUNT(DISTINCT r.topFrameDomainID) as countSubResourceUnderTopFrame, "
1220 "COUNT(DISTINCT toDomainID) as countUniqueRedirectTo "
1221 "FROM "
1222 "ObservedDomains o "
1223 "LEFT JOIN SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains f ON o.domainID = f.subFrameDomainID "
1224 "LEFT JOIN SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains r ON o.domainID = r.subresourceDomainID "
1225 "LEFT JOIN SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo u ON o.domainID = u.subresourceDomainID "
1226 "WHERE isPrevalent LIKE ? "
1227 "and hadUserInteraction LIKE ? "
1228 "GROUP BY domainID) ORDER BY sum DESC;"_s;
1229}
1230
1231Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstParty> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::getThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomains(unsigned thirdPartyDomainID, const RegistrableDomain& thirdPartyDomain) const
1232{
1233 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_getAllSubStatisticsStatement, getAllSubStatisticsUnderDomainQuery, "getThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomains"_s);
1234 if (!scopedStatement
1235 || scopedStatement->bindInt(1, thirdPartyDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
1236 || scopedStatement->bindInt(2, thirdPartyDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
1237 || scopedStatement->bindInt(3, thirdPartyDomainID) != SQLITE_OK) {
1238 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::getThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomain, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1239 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1240 }
1241 Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstParty> thirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomains;
1242 while (scopedStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1243 RegistrableDomain firstPartyDomain = RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(getDomainStringFromDomainID(m_getAllSubStatisticsStatement->columnInt(0)));
1244 thirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomains.appendIfNotContains(WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstParty { firstPartyDomain, hasStorageAccess(firstPartyDomain, thirdPartyDomain), getMostRecentlyUpdatedTimestamp(thirdPartyDomain, firstPartyDomain) });
1245 }
1246 return thirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomains;
1247}
1248
1249static bool hasBeenThirdParty(unsigned timesUnderFirstParty)
1250{
1251 return timesUnderFirstParty > 0;
1252}
1253
1254Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::aggregatedThirdPartyData() const
1255{
1256 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1257
1258 Vector<WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData> thirdPartyDataList;
1259 const auto prevalentDomainsBindParameter = thirdPartyCookieBlockingMode() == ThirdPartyCookieBlockingMode::All ? "%" : "1";
1260 auto sortedStatistics = m_database.prepareStatement(joinSubStatisticsForSorting());
1261 if (!sortedStatistics
1262 || sortedStatistics->bindText(1, prevalentDomainsBindParameter)
1263 || sortedStatistics->bindText(2, "%") != SQLITE_OK) {
1264 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::aggregatedThirdPartyData, error message: %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1265 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1266 return thirdPartyDataList;
1267 }
1268 while (sortedStatistics->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1269 if (hasBeenThirdParty(sortedStatistics->columnInt(1))) {
1270 auto thirdPartyDomainID = sortedStatistics->columnInt(0);
1271 auto thirdPartyDomain = RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(getDomainStringFromDomainID(thirdPartyDomainID));
1272 thirdPartyDataList.append(WebResourceLoadStatisticsStore::ThirdPartyData { thirdPartyDomain, getThirdPartyDataForSpecificFirstPartyDomains(thirdPartyDomainID, thirdPartyDomain) });
1273 }
1274 }
1275 return thirdPartyDataList;
1276}

1280 StringBuilder builder;
1281 for (const auto& domainName : domains)
1282 builder.append(builder.isEmpty() ? "" : ", ", '"', domainName.string(), '"');
1283 return builder.toString();

1296
1297unsigned ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::recursivelyFindNonPrevalentDomainsThatRedirectedToThisDomain(unsigned primaryDomainID, StdSet<unsigned>& nonPrevalentRedirectionSources, unsigned numberOfRecursiveCalls)
1298{
1299 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1300
1301 if (numberOfRecursiveCalls >= maxNumberOfRecursiveCallsInRedirectTraceBack) {
1302 RELEASE_LOG(ResourceLoadStatistics, "Hit %u recursive calls in redirect backtrace. Returning early.", maxNumberOfRecursiveCallsInRedirectTraceBack);
1303 return numberOfRecursiveCalls;
1304 }
1305
1306 ++numberOfRecursiveCalls;
1307
1308 StdSet<unsigned> newlyIdentifiedDomains;
1309 auto findSubresources = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom.fromDomainID from SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom INNER JOIN ObservedDomains ON ObservedDomains.domainID = SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom.fromDomainID WHERE subresourceDomainID = ? AND ObservedDomains.isPrevalent = 0"_s);
1310 if (!findSubresources || findSubresources->bindInt(1, primaryDomainID) != SQLITE_OK) {
1311 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::recursivelyFindNonPrevalentDomainsThatRedirectedToThisDomain failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1312 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1313 return 0;
1314 }
1315
1316 while (findSubresources->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1317 int newDomainID = findSubresources->columnInt(0);
1318 auto insertResult = nonPrevalentRedirectionSources.insert(newDomainID);
1319 if (insertResult.second)
1320 newlyIdentifiedDomains.insert(newDomainID);
1321 }
1322
1323 auto findTopFrames = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom.fromDomainID from TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom INNER JOIN ObservedDomains ON ObservedDomains.domainID = TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom.fromDomainID WHERE targetDomainID = ? AND ObservedDomains.isPrevalent = 0"_s);
1324 if (!findTopFrames
1325 || findTopFrames->bindInt(1, primaryDomainID) != SQLITE_OK) {
1326 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::recursivelyFindNonPrevalentDomainsThatRedirectedToThisDomain failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1327 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1328 return 0;
1329 }
1330
1331 while (findTopFrames->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1332 int newDomainID = findTopFrames->columnInt(0);
1333 auto insertResult = nonPrevalentRedirectionSources.insert(newDomainID);
1334 if (insertResult.second)
1335 newlyIdentifiedDomains.insert(newDomainID);
1336 }
1337
1338 if (newlyIdentifiedDomains.empty())
1339 return numberOfRecursiveCalls;
1340
1341 for (auto domainID : newlyIdentifiedDomains)
1342 numberOfRecursiveCalls = recursivelyFindNonPrevalentDomainsThatRedirectedToThisDomain(domainID, nonPrevalentRedirectionSources, numberOfRecursiveCalls);
1343
1344 return numberOfRecursiveCalls;
1345}
1346
1347template <typename IteratorType>
1348static String buildList(const WTF::IteratorRange<IteratorType>& values)
1349{
1350 StringBuilder builder;
1351 for (auto domainID : values)
1352 builder.append(builder.isEmpty() ? "" : ", ", domainID);
1353 return builder.toString();
1354}
1355
1356void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::markAsPrevalentIfHasRedirectedToPrevalent()
1357{
1358 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1359
1360 StdSet<unsigned> prevalentDueToRedirect;
1361 auto subresourceRedirectStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT DISTINCT SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo.subresourceDomainID FROM SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo JOIN ObservedDomains ON ObservedDomains.domainID = SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo.toDomainID AND ObservedDomains.isPrevalent = 1"_s);
1362 if (subresourceRedirectStatement) {
1363 while (subresourceRedirectStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
1364 prevalentDueToRedirect.insert(subresourceRedirectStatement->columnInt(0));
1365 }
1366
1367 auto topFrameRedirectStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT DISTINCT TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo.sourceDomainID FROM TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo JOIN ObservedDomains ON ObservedDomains.domainID = TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo.toDomainID AND ObservedDomains.isPrevalent = 1"_s);
1368 if (topFrameRedirectStatement) {
1369 while (topFrameRedirectStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
1370 prevalentDueToRedirect.insert(topFrameRedirectStatement->columnInt(0));
1371 }
1372
1373 auto markPrevalentStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("UPDATE ObservedDomains SET isPrevalent = 1 WHERE domainID IN (", buildList(WTF::IteratorRange<StdSet<unsigned>::iterator>(prevalentDueToRedirect.begin(), prevalentDueToRedirect.end())), ")"));
1374 if (!markPrevalentStatement || markPrevalentStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1375 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::markAsPrevalentIfHasRedirectedToPrevalent failed to execute, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1376 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1377 }
1378}
1379
1380HashMap<unsigned, ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::NotVeryPrevalentResources> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::findNotVeryPrevalentResources()
1381{
1382 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1383
1384 HashMap<unsigned, NotVeryPrevalentResources> results;
1385 auto notVeryPrevalentResourcesStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT domainID, registrableDomain, isPrevalent FROM ObservedDomains WHERE isVeryPrevalent = 0"_s);
1386 if (notVeryPrevalentResourcesStatement) {
1387 while (notVeryPrevalentResourcesStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1388 unsigned key = static_cast<unsigned>(notVeryPrevalentResourcesStatement->columnInt(0));
1389 NotVeryPrevalentResources value({ RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(notVeryPrevalentResourcesStatement->columnText(1))
1390 , notVeryPrevalentResourcesStatement->columnInt(2) ? ResourceLoadPrevalence::High : ResourceLoadPrevalence::Low
1391 , 0, 0, 0, 0 });
1392 results.add(key, value);
1393 }
1394 }
1395
1396 StringBuilder builder;
1397 for (auto value : results.keys())
1398 builder.append(builder.isEmpty() ? "" : ", ", value);
1399 auto domainIDsOfInterest = builder.toString();
1400
1401 auto subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("SELECT subresourceDomainID, COUNT(topFrameDomainID) FROM SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE subresourceDomainID IN (", domainIDsOfInterest, ") GROUP BY subresourceDomainID"));
1402 if (subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsStatement) {
1403 while (subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1404 unsigned domainID = static_cast<unsigned>(subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsStatement->columnInt(0));
1405 auto result = results.find(domainID);
1406 if (result != results.end())
1407 result->value.subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsCount = static_cast<unsigned>(subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsStatement->columnInt(1));
1408 }
1409 }
1410
1411 auto subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("SELECT subresourceDomainID, COUNT(toDomainID) FROM SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo WHERE subresourceDomainID IN (", domainIDsOfInterest, ") GROUP BY subresourceDomainID"));
1412 if (subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement) {
1413 while (subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1414 unsigned domainID = static_cast<unsigned>(subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement->columnInt(0));
1415 auto result = results.find(domainID);
1416 if (result != results.end())
1417 result->value.subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCount = static_cast<unsigned>(subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement->columnInt(1));
1418 }
1419 }
1420
1421 auto subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCountStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("SELECT subframeDomainID, COUNT(topFrameDomainID) FROM SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE subframeDomainID IN (", domainIDsOfInterest, ") GROUP BY subframeDomainID"));
1422 if (subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCountStatement) {
1423 while (subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCountStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1424 unsigned domainID = static_cast<unsigned>(subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCountStatement->columnInt(0));
1425 auto result = results.find(domainID);
1426 if (result != results.end())
1427 result->value.subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCount = static_cast<unsigned>(subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCountStatement->columnInt(1));
1428 }
1429 }
1430
1431 auto topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("SELECT sourceDomainID, COUNT(toDomainID) FROM TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo WHERE sourceDomainID IN (", domainIDsOfInterest, ") GROUP BY sourceDomainID"));
1432 if (topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement) {
1433 while (topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
1434 unsigned domainID = static_cast<unsigned>(topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement->columnInt(0));
1435 auto result = results.find(domainID);
1436 if (result != results.end())
1437 result->value.topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCount = static_cast<unsigned>(topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCountStatement->columnInt(1));
1438 }
1439 }
1440
1441 return results;
1442}

1444void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::reclassifyResources()
1445{
1446 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1447
1448 auto notVeryPrevalentResources = findNotVeryPrevalentResources();
1449 if (notVeryPrevalentResources.isEmpty())
1450 return;
1451
1452 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1453 for (auto& resourceStatistic : notVeryPrevalentResources.values()) {
1454 if (shouldSkip(resourceStatistic.registrableDomain))
1455 continue;
1456
1457 auto newPrevalence = classifier().calculateResourcePrevalence(resourceStatistic.subresourceUnderTopFrameDomainsCount, resourceStatistic.subresourceUniqueRedirectsToCount, resourceStatistic.subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsCount, resourceStatistic.topFrameUniqueRedirectsToCount, resourceStatistic.prevalence);
1458 if (newPrevalence != resourceStatistic.prevalence) {
1459 if (!transaction.inProgress())
1460 transaction.begin();
1461 setPrevalentResource(transaction, resourceStatistic.registrableDomain, newPrevalence);
1462 }
1463 }
1464 transaction.commit();
1465}
1466
1467void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::classifyPrevalentResources()
1468{
1469 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1470 ensurePrevalentResourcesForDebugMode();
1471 markAsPrevalentIfHasRedirectedToPrevalent();
1472 reclassifyResources();
1473}

1477 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1478 m_database.runIncrementalVacuumCommand();

1481bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasStorageAccess(const TopFrameDomain& topFrameDomain, const SubFrameDomain& subFrameDomain) const
1482{
1483 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_storageAccessExistsStatement, storageAccessExistsQuery, "hasStorageAccess"_s);
1484 return relationshipExists(scopedStatement, domainID(subFrameDomain), topFrameDomain);
1485}

1487void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasStorageAccess(const SubFrameDomain& subFrameDomain, const TopFrameDomain& topFrameDomain, std::optional<FrameIdentifier> frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, CompletionHandler<void(bool)>&& completionHandler)
1488{
1489 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1490
1491 auto result = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(subFrameDomain);
1492 if (!result.second) {
1493 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasStorageAccess was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1494 return;
1495 }
1496
1497 switch (cookieAccess(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain)) {
1498 case CookieAccess::CannotRequest:
1499 completionHandler(false);
1500 return;
1501 case CookieAccess::BasedOnCookiePolicy:
1502 RunLoop::main().dispatch([store = makeRef(store()), subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
1503 store->hasCookies(subFrameDomain, [store, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](bool result) mutable {
1504 store->statisticsQueue().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), result] () mutable {
1505 completionHandler(result);
1506 });
1507 });
1508 });
1509 return;
1510 case CookieAccess::OnlyIfGranted:
1511 // Handled below.
1512 break;
1513 };
1514
1515 RunLoop::main().dispatch([store = makeRef(store()), subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), frameID, pageID, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
1516 store->callHasStorageAccessForFrameHandler(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID.value(), pageID, [store, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](bool result) mutable {
1517 store->statisticsQueue().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), result] () mutable {
1518 completionHandler(result);
1519 });
1520 });
1521 });
1522}
1523
1524void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::requestStorageAccess(SubFrameDomain&& subFrameDomain, TopFrameDomain&& topFrameDomain, FrameIdentifier frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(StorageAccessStatus)>&& completionHandler)
1525{
1526 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1527
1528 auto subFrameStatus = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(subFrameDomain);
1529 if (!subFrameStatus.second) {
1530 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::requestStorageAccess was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1531 return;
1532 }
1533
1534 switch (cookieAccess(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain)) {
1535 case CookieAccess::CannotRequest:
1536 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
1537 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "Cannot grant storage access to %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " since its cookies are blocked in third-party contexts and it has not received user interaction as first-party.", subFrameDomain.string().utf8().data());
1538 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Error, makeString("[ITP] Cannot grant storage access to '"_s, subFrameDomain.string(), "' since its cookies are blocked in third-party contexts and it has not received user interaction as first-party."_s));
1539 }
1540 completionHandler(StorageAccessStatus::CannotRequestAccess);
1541 return;
1542 case CookieAccess::BasedOnCookiePolicy:
1543 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
1544 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "No need to grant storage access to %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " since its cookies are not blocked in third-party contexts. Note that the underlying cookie policy may still block this third-party from setting cookies.", subFrameDomain.string().utf8().data());
1545 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[ITP] No need to grant storage access to '"_s, subFrameDomain.string(), "' since its cookies are not blocked in third-party contexts. Note that the underlying cookie policy may still block this third-party from setting cookies."_s));
1546 }
1547 completionHandler(StorageAccessStatus::HasAccess);
1548 return;
1549 case CookieAccess::OnlyIfGranted:
1550 // Handled below.
1551 break;
1552 }
1553
1554 auto userWasPromptedEarlier = hasUserGrantedStorageAccessThroughPrompt(*subFrameStatus.second, topFrameDomain);
1555 if (userWasPromptedEarlier == StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No) {
1556 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
1557 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "About to ask the user whether they want to grant storage access to %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " under %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " or not.", subFrameDomain.string().utf8().data(), topFrameDomain.string().utf8().data());
1558 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[ITP] About to ask the user whether they want to grant storage access to '"_s, subFrameDomain.string(), "' under '"_s, topFrameDomain.string(), "' or not."_s));
1559 }
1560 completionHandler(StorageAccessStatus::RequiresUserPrompt);
1561 return;
1562 }
1563
1564 if (userWasPromptedEarlier == StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes) {
1565 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
1566 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "Storage access was granted to %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " under %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING ".", subFrameDomain.string().utf8().data(), topFrameDomain.string().utf8().data());
1567 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[ITP] Storage access was granted to '"_s, subFrameDomain.string(), "' under '"_s, topFrameDomain.string(), "'."_s));
1568 }
1569 }
1570
1571 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1572 transaction.begin();
1573
1574 auto incrementStorageAccess = m_database.prepareStatement("UPDATE ObservedDomains SET timesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPI = timesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPI + 1 WHERE domainID = ?"_s);
1575 if (!incrementStorageAccess
1576 || incrementStorageAccess->bindInt(1, *subFrameStatus.second) != SQLITE_OK
1577 || incrementStorageAccess->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1578 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::requestStorageAccess failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1579 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1580 return;
1581 }
1582
1583 grantStorageAccessInternal(transaction, WTFMove(subFrameDomain), WTFMove(topFrameDomain), frameID, pageID, userWasPromptedEarlier, scope, [completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (StorageAccessWasGranted wasGranted) mutable {
1584 completionHandler(wasGranted == StorageAccessWasGranted::Yes ? StorageAccessStatus::HasAccess : StorageAccessStatus::CannotRequestAccess);
1585 });
1586
1587 transaction.commit();
1588}
1589
1590void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::requestStorageAccessUnderOpener(DomainInNeedOfStorageAccess&& domainInNeedOfStorageAccess, PageIdentifier openerPageID, OpenerDomain&& openerDomain)
1591{
1592 ASSERT(domainInNeedOfStorageAccess != openerDomain);
1593 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1594
1595 if (domainInNeedOfStorageAccess == openerDomain)
1596 return;
1597
1598 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
1599 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "[Temporary combatibility fix] Storage access was granted for %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " under opener page from %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING ", with user interaction in the opened window.", domainInNeedOfStorageAccess.string().utf8().data(), openerDomain.string().utf8().data());
1600 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[ITP] Storage access was granted for '"_s, domainInNeedOfStorageAccess.string(), "' under opener page from '"_s, openerDomain.string(), "', with user interaction in the opened window."_s));
1601 }
1602
1603 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1604 transaction.begin();
1605 grantStorageAccessInternal(transaction, WTFMove(domainInNeedOfStorageAccess), WTFMove(openerDomain), std::nullopt, openerPageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No, StorageAccessScope::PerPage, [](StorageAccessWasGranted) { });
1606 transaction.commit();
1607}

1609void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grantStorageAccess(SubFrameDomain&& subFrameDomain, TopFrameDomain&& topFrameDomain, FrameIdentifier frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown promptWasShown, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(StorageAccessWasGranted)>&& completionHandler)
1610{
1611 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1612
1613 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1614 transaction.begin();
1615
1616 if (promptWasShown == StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes) {
1617 auto subFrameStatus = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(subFrameDomain);
1618 if (!subFrameStatus.second) {
1619 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grantStorageAccess was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1620 return;
1621 }
1622 ASSERT(subFrameStatus.first == AddedRecord::No);
1623#if ASSERT_ENABLED
1624 if (!NetworkStorageSession::canRequestStorageAccessForLoginOrCompatibilityPurposesWithoutPriorUserInteraction(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain))
1625 ASSERT(hasHadUserInteraction(subFrameDomain, OperatingDatesWindow::Long));
1626#endif
1627 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, storageAccessUnderTopFrameDomainsQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ topFrameDomain }), *subFrameStatus.second);
1628 }
1629
1630 grantStorageAccessInternal(transaction, WTFMove(subFrameDomain), WTFMove(topFrameDomain), frameID, pageID, promptWasShown, scope, WTFMove(completionHandler));
1631
1632 transaction.commit();
1633}

1635void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grantStorageAccessInternal(const SQLiteTransaction& transaction, SubFrameDomain&& subFrameDomain, TopFrameDomain&& topFrameDomain, std::optional<FrameIdentifier> frameID, PageIdentifier pageID, StorageAccessPromptWasShown promptWasShownNowOrEarlier, StorageAccessScope scope, CompletionHandler<void(StorageAccessWasGranted)>&& completionHandler)
1636{
1637 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1638 ASSERT(m_database.transactionInProgress());
1639
1640 if (subFrameDomain == topFrameDomain) {
1641 completionHandler(StorageAccessWasGranted::Yes);
1642 return;
1643 }
1644
1645 if (promptWasShownNowOrEarlier == StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes) {
1646#ifndef NDEBUG
1647 auto subFrameStatus = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(subFrameDomain);
1648 if (!subFrameStatus.second) {
1649 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grantStorageAccessInternal was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1650 return;
1651 }
1652 ASSERT(subFrameStatus.first == AddedRecord::No);
1653#if ASSERT_ENABLED
1654 if (!NetworkStorageSession::canRequestStorageAccessForLoginOrCompatibilityPurposesWithoutPriorUserInteraction(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain))
1655 ASSERT(hasHadUserInteraction(subFrameDomain, OperatingDatesWindow::Long));
1656#endif
1657 ASSERT(hasUserGrantedStorageAccessThroughPrompt(*subFrameStatus.second, topFrameDomain) == StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes);
1658#endif
1659 setUserInteraction(subFrameDomain, true, WallTime::now());
1660 }
1661
1662 RunLoop::main().dispatch([subFrameDomain = subFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), topFrameDomain = topFrameDomain.isolatedCopy(), frameID, pageID, store = makeRef(store()), scope, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
1663 store->callGrantStorageAccessHandler(subFrameDomain, topFrameDomain, frameID, pageID, scope, [completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), store](StorageAccessWasGranted wasGranted) mutable {
1664 store->statisticsQueue().dispatch([wasGranted, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] () mutable {
1665 completionHandler(wasGranted);
1666 });
1667 });
1668 });
1669
1670}

1672void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grandfatherDataForDomains(const HashSet<RegistrableDomain>& domains)
1673{
1674 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1675 if (domains.isEmpty())
1676 return;
1677
1678 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1679 transaction.begin();
1680 for (auto& registrableDomain : domains) {
1681 auto result = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(registrableDomain);
1682 if (!result.second)
1683 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grandfatherDataForDomains was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1684 }
1685
1686 auto domainsToUpdateStatement = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("UPDATE ObservedDomains SET grandfathered = 1 WHERE registrableDomain IN (", domainsToString(domains), ")"));
1687 if (!domainsToUpdateStatement || domainsToUpdateStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1688 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::grandfatherDataForDomains failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1689 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1690 }
1691 transaction.commit();
1692}
