1694Vector<RegistrableDomain> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensurePrevalentResourcesForDebugMode()
1695{
1696 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1697
1698 if (!debugModeEnabled())
1699 return { };
1700
1701 Vector<RegistrableDomain> primaryDomainsToBlock;
1702 primaryDomainsToBlock.reserveInitialCapacity(2);
1703
1704 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1705 transaction.begin();
1706
1707 auto result = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(debugStaticPrevalentResource());
1708 if (!result.second) {
1709 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensurePrevalentResourcesForDebugMode was not completed due to failed insert attempt for debugStaticPrevalentResource", this);
1710 return { };
1711 }
1712
1713 setPrevalentResource(transaction, debugStaticPrevalentResource(), ResourceLoadPrevalence::High);
1714 primaryDomainsToBlock.uncheckedAppend(debugStaticPrevalentResource());
1715
1716 if (!debugManualPrevalentResource().isEmpty()) {
1717 auto result = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(debugManualPrevalentResource());
1718 if (!result.second) {
1719 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensurePrevalentResourcesForDebugMode was not completed due to failed insert attempt for debugManualPrevalentResource", this);
1720 return { };
1721 }
1722 setPrevalentResource(transaction, debugManualPrevalentResource(), ResourceLoadPrevalence::High);
1723 primaryDomainsToBlock.uncheckedAppend(debugManualPrevalentResource());
1724
1725 if (debugLoggingEnabled()) {
1726 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "Did set %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING " as prevalent resource for the purposes of ITP Debug Mode.", debugManualPrevalentResource().string().utf8().data());
1727 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[ITP] Did set '"_s, debugManualPrevalentResource().string(), "' as prevalent resource for the purposes of ITP Debug Mode."_s));
1728 }
1729 }
1730
1731 transaction.commit();
1732
1733 return primaryDomainsToBlock;
1734}
1735
1736void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logFrameNavigation(const RegistrableDomain& targetDomain, const RegistrableDomain& topFrameDomain, const RegistrableDomain& sourceDomain, bool isRedirect, bool isMainFrame, Seconds delayAfterMainFrameDocumentLoad, bool wasPotentiallyInitiatedByUser)
1737{
1738 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1739
1740 bool areTargetAndTopFrameDomainsSameSite = targetDomain == topFrameDomain;
1741 bool areTargetAndSourceDomainsSameSite = targetDomain == sourceDomain;
1742
1743 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1744
1745 bool statisticsWereUpdated = false;
1746 if (!isMainFrame && !(areTargetAndTopFrameDomainsSameSite || areTargetAndSourceDomainsSameSite)) {
1747 if (!transaction.inProgress())
1748 transaction.begin();
1749
1750 auto targetResult = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(targetDomain);
1751 if (!targetResult.second) {
1752 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logFrameNavigation was not completed due to failed insert attempt of target domain", this);
1753 return;
1754 }
1755 updateLastSeen(targetDomain, ResourceLoadStatistics::reduceTimeResolution(WallTime::now()));
1756 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subframeUnderTopFrameDomainsQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ topFrameDomain }), *targetResult.second);
1757 statisticsWereUpdated = true;
1758 }
1759
1760 if (!areTargetAndSourceDomainsSameSite) {
1761 if (isMainFrame) {
1762 bool wasNavigatedAfterShortDelayWithoutUserInteraction = !wasPotentiallyInitiatedByUser && delayAfterMainFrameDocumentLoad < parameters().minDelayAfterMainFrameDocumentLoadToNotBeARedirect;
1763 if (isRedirect || wasNavigatedAfterShortDelayWithoutUserInteraction) {
1764 if (!transaction.inProgress())
1765 transaction.begin();
1766
1767 auto redirectingDomainResult = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(sourceDomain);
1768 auto targetResult = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(targetDomain);
1769 if (!targetResult.second || !redirectingDomainResult.second) {
1770 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logFrameNavigation was not completed due to failed insert attempt of target or redirecting domain (isMainFrame)", this);
1771 return;
1772 }
1773 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameUniqueRedirectsToQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ targetDomain }), *redirectingDomainResult.second);
1774 if (isRedirect) {
1775 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcementQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ targetDomain }), *redirectingDomainResult.second);
1776
1777 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
1778 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "Did set %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING " as making a top frame redirect to %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING ".", sourceDomain.string().utf8().data(), targetDomain.string().utf8().data());
1779 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("Did set '", sourceDomain.string(), "' as making a top frame redirect to '", targetDomain.string(), "'."));
1780 }
1781 }
1782 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, topFrameUniqueRedirectsFromQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ sourceDomain }), *targetResult.second);
1783 statisticsWereUpdated = true;
1784 }
1785 } else if (isRedirect) {
1786 if (!transaction.inProgress())
1787 transaction.begin();
1788
1789 auto redirectingDomainResult = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(sourceDomain);
1790 auto targetResult = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(targetDomain);
1791 if (!targetResult.second || !redirectingDomainResult.second) {
1792 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logFrameNavigation was not completed due to failed insert attempt of target or redirecting domain (isRedirect)", this);
1793 return;
1794 }
1795 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subresourceUniqueRedirectsToQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ targetDomain }), *redirectingDomainResult.second);
1796 insertDomainRelationshipList(transaction, subresourceUniqueRedirectsFromQuery, HashSet<RegistrableDomain>({ sourceDomain }), *targetResult.second);
1797 statisticsWereUpdated = true;
1798 }
1799 }
1800 transaction.commit();
1801
1802 if (statisticsWereUpdated)
1803 scheduleStatisticsProcessingRequestIfNecessary();
1804}

1806void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logCrossSiteLoadWithLinkDecoration(const NavigatedFromDomain& fromDomain, const NavigatedToDomain& toDomain)
1807{

1809 ASSERT(fromDomain != toDomain);
1810
1811 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);

1813

1815 if (!toDomainResult.second) {

1820

1869
1870void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logUserInteraction(const TopFrameDomain& domain, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1871{
1872 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1873
1874 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1875 transaction.begin();
1876
1877 auto result = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(domain);
1878 if (!result.second) {
1879 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::logUserInteraction was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1880 return;
1881 }
1882 bool didHavePreviousUserInteraction = hasHadUserInteraction(domain, OperatingDatesWindow::Long);
1883 setUserInteraction(domain, true, WallTime::now());
1884
1885 transaction.commit();
1886
1887 if (didHavePreviousUserInteraction) {
1888 completionHandler();
1889 return;
1890 }
1891 updateCookieBlocking(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1892}
1893
1894void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::clearUserInteraction(const RegistrableDomain& domain, CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
1895{
1896 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1897
1898 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
1899 transaction.begin();
1900
1901 auto targetResult = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(domain);
1902 if (!targetResult.second) {
1903 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::clearUserInteraction was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
1904 return;
1905 }
1906 setUserInteraction(domain, false, { });
1907
1908 auto removeStorageAccess = m_database.prepareStatement("DELETE FROM StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE domainID = ?"_s);
1909 if (!removeStorageAccess
1910 || removeStorageAccess->bindInt(1, *targetResult.second) != SQLITE_OK
1911 || removeStorageAccess->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1912 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::clearUserInteraction failed to bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1913 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1914 }
1915
1916 transaction.commit();
1917
1918 // Update cookie blocking unconditionally since a call to hasHadUserInteraction()
1919 // to check the previous user interaction status could call clearUserInteraction(),
1920 // blowing the call stack.
1921 updateCookieBlocking(WTFMove(completionHandler));
1922}
1923
1924bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasHadUserInteraction(const RegistrableDomain& domain, OperatingDatesWindow operatingDatesWindow)
1925{
1926 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1927
1928 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_hadUserInteractionStatement, hadUserInteractionQuery, "hasHadUserInteraction"_s);
1929 if (!scopedStatement
1930 || scopedStatement->bindText(1, domain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
1931 || scopedStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
1932 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::m_hadUserInteractionStatement failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1933 return false;
1934 }
1935
1936 bool hadUserInteraction = !!scopedStatement->columnInt(0);
1937 if (!hadUserInteraction)
1938 return false;
1939
1940 WallTime mostRecentUserInteractionTime = WallTime::fromRawSeconds(scopedStatement->columnDouble(1));
1941
1942 if (hasStatisticsExpired(mostRecentUserInteractionTime, operatingDatesWindow)) {
1943 // Drop privacy sensitive data because we no longer need it.
1944 // Set timestamp to 0 so that statistics merge will know
1945 // it has been reset as opposed to its default -1.
1946 clearUserInteraction(domain, [] { });
1947 hadUserInteraction = false;
1948 }
1949 return hadUserInteraction;
1950}

1952void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::setPrevalentResource(const SQLiteTransaction&, const RegistrableDomain& domain, ResourceLoadPrevalence newPrevalence)
1953{
1954 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
1955 ASSERT(m_database.transactionInProgress());
1956
1957 if (shouldSkip(domain))
1958 return;
1959
1960 auto registrableDomainID = domainID(domain);
1961 if (!registrableDomainID) {
1962 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::setPrevalentResource domainID should exist but was not found.", this);
1963 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1964 return;
1965 }
1966
1967 auto scopedUpdatePrevalentResourceStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_updatePrevalentResourceStatement, updatePrevalentResourceQuery, "setPrevalentResource"_s);
1968 if (!scopedUpdatePrevalentResourceStatement
1969 || scopedUpdatePrevalentResourceStatement->bindInt(1, 1) != SQLITE_OK
1970 || scopedUpdatePrevalentResourceStatement->bindText(2, domain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
1971 || scopedUpdatePrevalentResourceStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1972 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::m_updatePrevalentResourceStatement failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1973 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1974 return;
1975 }
1976
1977 auto scopedUpdateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_updateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement, updateVeryPrevalentResourceQuery, "setPrevalentResource updateVeryPrevalentResource"_s);
1978 if (newPrevalence == ResourceLoadPrevalence::VeryHigh) {
1979 if (!scopedUpdateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement
1980 || scopedUpdateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement->bindInt(1, 1) != SQLITE_OK
1981 || scopedUpdateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement->bindText(2, domain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
1982 || scopedUpdateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
1983 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::m_updateVeryPrevalentResourceStatement failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
1984 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1985 return;
1986 }
1987 }
1988
1989 StdSet<unsigned> nonPrevalentRedirectionSources;
1990 recursivelyFindNonPrevalentDomainsThatRedirectedToThisDomain(*registrableDomainID, nonPrevalentRedirectionSources, 0);
1991 setDomainsAsPrevalent(WTFMove(nonPrevalentRedirectionSources));
1992}

2006void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::dumpResourceLoadStatistics(CompletionHandler<void(const String&)>&& completionHandler)
2007{
2008 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2009 if (dataRecordsBeingRemoved()) {
2010 m_dataRecordRemovalCompletionHandlers.append([this, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
2011 dumpResourceLoadStatistics(WTFMove(completionHandler));
2012 });
2013 return;
2014 }
2015
2016 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_getAllDomainsStatement, getAllDomainsQuery, "dumpResourceLoadStatistics"_s);
2017 if (!scopedStatement)
2018 return;
2019
2020 Vector<String> domains;
2021 while (scopedStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
2022 domains.append(scopedStatement->columnText(0));
2023 std::sort(domains.begin(), domains.end(), WTF::codePointCompareLessThan);
2024
2025 StringBuilder result;
2026 result.append("Resource load statistics:\n\n");
2027 for (auto& domain : domains)
2028 resourceToString(result, domain);
2029
2030 auto thirdPartyData = aggregatedThirdPartyData();
2031 if (!thirdPartyData.isEmpty()) {
2032 result.append("\nITP Data:\n");
2033 for (auto thirdParty : thirdPartyData)
2034 result.append(thirdParty.toString(), '\n');
2035 }
2036 completionHandler(result.toString());
2037}

2176Seconds ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::getMostRecentlyUpdatedTimestamp(const RegistrableDomain& subDomain, const TopFrameDomain& topFrameDomain) const
2177{
2178 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2179
2180 std::optional<unsigned> subFrameDomainID = domainID(subDomain);
2181 std::optional<unsigned> topFrameDomainID = domainID(topFrameDomain);
2182
2183 if (!subFrameDomainID || !topFrameDomainID)
2184 return Seconds { ResourceLoadStatistics::NoExistingTimestamp };
2185
2186 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_getMostRecentlyUpdatedTimestampStatement, getMostRecentlyUpdatedTimestampQuery, "getMostRecentlyUpdatedTimestamp"_s);
2187 if (!scopedStatement
2188 || scopedStatement->bindInt(1, *subFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2189 || scopedStatement->bindInt(2, *topFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2190 || scopedStatement->bindInt(3, *subFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2191 || scopedStatement->bindInt(4, *topFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2192 || scopedStatement->bindInt(5, *subFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2193 || scopedStatement->bindInt(6, *topFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2194 || scopedStatement->bindInt(7, *subFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2195 || scopedStatement->bindInt(8, *topFrameDomainID) != SQLITE_OK) {
2196 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::getMostRecentlyUpdatedTimestamp failed to bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2197 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2198 return Seconds { ResourceLoadStatistics::NoExistingTimestamp };
2199 }
2200 if (scopedStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW)
2201 return Seconds { ResourceLoadStatistics::NoExistingTimestamp };
2202
2203 return Seconds { scopedStatement->columnDouble(0) };
2204}

2323std::pair<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::AddedRecord, std::optional<unsigned>> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(const RegistrableDomain& domain)
2324{
2325 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2326
2327 {
2328 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_domainIDFromStringStatement, domainIDFromStringQuery, "ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain"_s);
2329 if (!scopedStatement
2330 || scopedStatement->bindText(1, domain.string()) != SQLITE_OK) {
2331 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2332 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2333 return { AddedRecord::No, 0 };
2334 }
2335
2336 if (scopedStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
2337 unsigned domainID = scopedStatement->columnInt(0);
2338 return { AddedRecord::No, domainID };
2339 }
2340 }
2341
2342 ResourceLoadStatistics newObservation(domain);
2343 auto result = insertObservedDomain(newObservation);
2344
2345 if (!result) {
2346 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain insertObservedDomain failed to complete, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2347 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2348 return { AddedRecord::No, std::nullopt };
2349 }
2350

2410bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::areAllThirdPartyCookiesBlockedUnder(const TopFrameDomain& topFrameDomain)
2411{
2412 if (thirdPartyCookieBlockingMode() == ThirdPartyCookieBlockingMode::All)
2413 return true;
2414
2415 if (thirdPartyCookieBlockingMode() == ThirdPartyCookieBlockingMode::AllOnSitesWithoutUserInteraction && !hasHadUserInteraction(topFrameDomain, OperatingDatesWindow::Long))
2416 return true;
2417
2418 return false;
2419}
2420
2421CookieAccess ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::cookieAccess(const SubResourceDomain& subresourceDomain, const TopFrameDomain& topFrameDomain)
2422{
2423 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2424
2425 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT isPrevalent, hadUserInteraction FROM ObservedDomains WHERE registrableDomain = ?"_s);
2426 if (!statement || statement->bindText(1, subresourceDomain.string()) != SQLITE_OK) {
2427 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::cookieAccess failed to bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2428 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2429 }
2430
2431 bool hasNoEntry = statement->step() != SQLITE_ROW;
2432 bool isPrevalent = !hasNoEntry && !!statement->columnInt(0);
2433 bool hadUserInteraction = !hasNoEntry && statement->columnInt(1) ? true : false;
2434
2435 if (!areAllThirdPartyCookiesBlockedUnder(topFrameDomain) && !isPrevalent)
2436 return CookieAccess::BasedOnCookiePolicy;
2437
2438 if (!NetworkStorageSession::canRequestStorageAccessForLoginOrCompatibilityPurposesWithoutPriorUserInteraction(subresourceDomain, topFrameDomain) && !hadUserInteraction)
2439 return CookieAccess::CannotRequest;
2440
2441 return CookieAccess::OnlyIfGranted;
2442}
2443
2444StorageAccessPromptWasShown ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasUserGrantedStorageAccessThroughPrompt(unsigned requestingDomainID, const RegistrableDomain& firstPartyDomain)
2445{
2446 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2447
2448 auto result = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(firstPartyDomain);
2449 if (!result.second) {
2450 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasUserGrantedStorageAccessThroughPrompt was not completed due to failed insert attempt", this);
2451 return StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No;
2452 }
2453
2454 auto firstPartyPrimaryDomainID = *result.second;
2455
2456 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE domainID = ? AND topLevelDomainID = ?"_s);
2457 if (!statement
2458 || statement->bindInt(1, requestingDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2459 || statement->bindInt(2, firstPartyPrimaryDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
2460 || statement->step() != SQLITE_ROW)
2461 return StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No;
2462
2463 return !!statement->columnInt(0) ? StorageAccessPromptWasShown::Yes : StorageAccessPromptWasShown::No;
2464}

2511HashMap<TopFrameDomain, SubResourceDomain> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::domainsWithStorageAccess() const
2512{
2513 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2514
2515 HashMap<WebCore::RegistrableDomain, WebCore::RegistrableDomain> results;
2516 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT subFrameDomain, registrableDomain FROM (SELECT o.registrableDomain as subFrameDomain, s.topLevelDomainID as topLevelDomainID FROM ObservedDomains as o INNER JOIN StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains as s WHERE o.domainID = s.domainID) as z INNER JOIN ObservedDomains ON domainID = z.topLevelDomainID;"_s);
2517 if (!statement)
2518 return results;
2519
2520 while (statement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
2521 results.add(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(statement->columnText(1)), RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(statement->columnText(0)));

2525
2526void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateCookieBlocking(CompletionHandler<void()>&& completionHandler)
2527{
2528 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2529
2530 auto domainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor = this->domainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor();
2531 auto domainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor = this->domainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor();
2532 auto domainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty = this->domainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty();
2533 auto domainsWithStorageAccess = this->domainsWithStorageAccess();
2534
2535 if (domainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor.isEmpty() && domainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor.isEmpty() && domainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty.isEmpty() && domainsWithStorageAccess.isEmpty()) {
2536 completionHandler();
2537 return;
2538 }
2539
2540 RegistrableDomainsToBlockCookiesFor domainsToBlock { domainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor, domainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor, domainsWithUserInteractionAsFirstParty, domainsWithStorageAccess };
2541
2542 if (debugLoggingEnabled() && (!domainsToBlockAndDeleteCookiesFor.isEmpty() || !domainsToBlockButKeepCookiesFor.isEmpty()))
2543 debugLogDomainsInBatches("Applying cross-site tracking restrictions", domainsToBlock);
2544
2545 RunLoop::main().dispatch([weakThis = makeWeakPtr(*this), store = makeRef(store()), domainsToBlock = crossThreadCopy(domainsToBlock), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] () mutable {
2546 store->callUpdatePrevalentDomainsToBlockCookiesForHandler(domainsToBlock, [weakThis = WTFMove(weakThis), store, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
2547 store->statisticsQueue().dispatch([weakThis = WTFMove(weakThis), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
2548 completionHandler();
2549
2550 if (!weakThis)
2551 return;
2552
2553 if (UNLIKELY(weakThis->debugLoggingEnabled())) {
2554 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "Done applying cross-site tracking restrictions.");
2555 weakThis->debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, "[ITP] Done applying cross-site tracking restrictions."_s);
2556 }
2557 });
2558 });
2559 });
2560}
2561
2562Vector<ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::DomainData> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::domains() const
2563{
2564 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2565
2566 Vector<DomainData> results;
2567 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT domainID, registrableDomain, mostRecentUserInteractionTime, hadUserInteraction, grandfathered, isScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval, countOfTopFrameRedirects FROM ObservedDomains LEFT JOIN (SELECT sourceDomainID, COUNT(*) as countOfTopFrameRedirects from TopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement GROUP BY sourceDomainID) as z ON z.sourceDomainID = domainID"_s);
2568 if (!statement)
2569 return results;
2570
2571 while (statement->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
2572 results.append({ static_cast<unsigned>(statement->columnInt(0))
2573 , RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(statement->columnText(1))
2574 , WallTime::fromRawSeconds(statement->columnDouble(2))
2575 , statement->columnInt(3) ? true : false
2576 , statement->columnInt(4) ? true : false
2577 , statement->columnInt(5) ? true : false
2578 , static_cast<unsigned>(statement->columnInt(6))
2579 });
2580 }
2581
2582 return results;
2583}

2601 }
2602}

2604bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasHadUnexpiredRecentUserInteraction(const DomainData& resourceStatistic, OperatingDatesWindow operatingDatesWindow)
2605{
2606 if (resourceStatistic.hadUserInteraction && hasStatisticsExpired(resourceStatistic.mostRecentUserInteractionTime, operatingDatesWindow)) {
2607
2608 // Drop privacy sensitive data if we no longer need it.
2609 if (operatingDatesWindow == OperatingDatesWindow::Long)
2610 clearUserInteraction(resourceStatistic.registrableDomain, [] { });
2611
2612 return false;
2613 }
2614
2615 return resourceStatistic.hadUserInteraction;
2616}
2617
2618bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::shouldRemoveAllWebsiteDataFor(const DomainData& resourceStatistic, bool shouldCheckForGrandfathering)
2619{
2620 return isPrevalentResource(resourceStatistic.registrableDomain) && !hasHadUnexpiredRecentUserInteraction(resourceStatistic, OperatingDatesWindow::Long) && (!shouldCheckForGrandfathering || !resourceStatistic.grandfathered);
2621}
2622
2623bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::shouldRemoveAllButCookiesFor(const DomainData& resourceStatistic, bool shouldCheckForGrandfathering)
2624{
2625 bool isRemovalEnabled = firstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode() != FirstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode::None || resourceStatistic.isScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval;
2626 bool isResourceGrandfathered = shouldCheckForGrandfathering && resourceStatistic.grandfathered;
2627
2628 OperatingDatesWindow window { };
2629 switch (firstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode()) {
2630 case FirstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode::AllButCookies:
2631 FALLTHROUGH;
2632 case FirstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode::None:
2633 window = OperatingDatesWindow::Short;
2634 break;
2635 case FirstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode::AllButCookiesLiveOnTestingTimeout:
2636 window = OperatingDatesWindow::ForLiveOnTesting;
2637 break;
2638 case FirstPartyWebsiteDataRemovalMode::AllButCookiesReproTestingTimeout:
2639 window = OperatingDatesWindow::ForReproTesting;
2640 }
2641
2642 return isRemovalEnabled && !isResourceGrandfathered && !hasHadUnexpiredRecentUserInteraction(resourceStatistic, window);
2643}
2644
2645bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::shouldEnforceSameSiteStrictFor(DomainData& resourceStatistic, bool shouldCheckForGrandfathering)
2646{
2647 if ((!isSameSiteStrictEnforcementEnabled() && !shouldEnforceSameSiteStrictForSpecificDomain(resourceStatistic.registrableDomain))
2648 || (shouldCheckForGrandfathering && resourceStatistic.grandfathered))
2649 return false;
2650
2651 if (resourceStatistic.topFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement > parameters().minimumTopFrameRedirectsForSameSiteStrictEnforcement) {
2652 clearTopFrameUniqueRedirectsToSinceSameSiteStrictEnforcement(resourceStatistic.registrableDomain, [] { });
2653 return true;
2654 }
2655
2656 return false;
2657}
2658
2659std::optional<WallTime> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::mostRecentUserInteractionTime(const DomainData& statistic)
2660{
2661 if (statistic.mostRecentUserInteractionTime.secondsSinceEpoch().value() <= 0)
2662 return std::nullopt;
2663
2664 return statistic.mostRecentUserInteractionTime;
2665}
2666
2667RegistrableDomainsToDeleteOrRestrictWebsiteDataFor ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::registrableDomainsToDeleteOrRestrictWebsiteDataFor()
2668{
2669 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2670
2671 bool shouldCheckForGrandfathering = endOfGrandfatheringTimestamp() > WallTime::now();
2672 bool shouldClearGrandfathering = !shouldCheckForGrandfathering && endOfGrandfatheringTimestamp();
2673
2674 if (shouldClearGrandfathering)
2675 clearEndOfGrandfatheringTimeStamp();
2676
2677 auto now = WallTime::now();
2678 auto oldestUserInteraction = now;
2679 RegistrableDomainsToDeleteOrRestrictWebsiteDataFor toDeleteOrRestrictFor;
2680
2681 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
2682
2683 Vector<DomainData> domains = this->domains();
2684 Vector<unsigned> domainIDsToClearGrandfathering;
2685 for (auto& statistic : domains) {
2686 if (shouldExemptFromWebsiteDataDeletion(statistic.registrableDomain))
2687 continue;
2688 if (auto mostRecentUserInteractionTime = this->mostRecentUserInteractionTime(statistic))
2689 oldestUserInteraction = std::min(oldestUserInteraction, *mostRecentUserInteractionTime);
2690 if (shouldRemoveAllWebsiteDataFor(statistic, shouldCheckForGrandfathering)) {
2691 toDeleteOrRestrictFor.domainsToDeleteAllCookiesFor.append(statistic.registrableDomain);
2692 toDeleteOrRestrictFor.domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.append(statistic.registrableDomain);
2693 } else {
2694 if (shouldRemoveAllButCookiesFor(statistic, shouldCheckForGrandfathering)) {
2695 toDeleteOrRestrictFor.domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.append(statistic.registrableDomain);
2696 if (!transaction.inProgress())
2697 transaction.begin();
2698 setIsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval(transaction, statistic.registrableDomain, false);
2699 }
2700 if (shouldEnforceSameSiteStrictFor(statistic, shouldCheckForGrandfathering)) {
2701 toDeleteOrRestrictFor.domainsToEnforceSameSiteStrictFor.append(statistic.registrableDomain);
2702
2703 if (UNLIKELY(debugLoggingEnabled())) {
2704 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(ITPDebug, "Scheduled %" PUBLIC_LOG_STRING " to have its cookies set to SameSite=strict.", statistic.registrableDomain.string().utf8().data());
2705 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::ITPDebug, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("Scheduled '", statistic.registrableDomain.string(), "' to have its cookies set to SameSite=strict'."));
2706 }
2707 }
2708 }
2709 if (shouldClearGrandfathering && statistic.grandfathered)
2710 domainIDsToClearGrandfathering.append(statistic.domainID);
2711 }
2712
2713 // Give the user enough time to interact with websites until we remove non-cookie website data.
2714 if (!parameters().isRunningTest && now - oldestUserInteraction < parameters().minimumTimeBetweenDataRecordsRemoval)
2715 toDeleteOrRestrictFor.domainsToDeleteAllNonCookieWebsiteDataFor.clear();
2716
2717 clearGrandfathering(WTFMove(domainIDsToClearGrandfathering));
2718
2719 transaction.commit();
2720
2721 return toDeleteOrRestrictFor;
2722}
2723
2724void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::pruneStatisticsIfNeeded()
2725{
2726 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
2727
2728 unsigned count = 0;
2729 auto scopedStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_observedDomainCountStatement, observedDomainCountQuery, "pruneStatisticsIfNeeded"_s);
2730 if (!scopedStatement)
2731 return;
2732
2733 if (scopedStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
2734 count = scopedStatement->columnInt(0);
2735
2736 if (count <= parameters().maxStatisticsEntries)
2737 return;
2738
2739 ASSERT(parameters().pruneEntriesDownTo <= parameters().maxStatisticsEntries);
2740
2741 size_t countLeftToPrune = count - parameters().pruneEntriesDownTo;
2742 ASSERT(countLeftToPrune);
2743
2744 auto recordsToPrune = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT domainID FROM ObservedDomains ORDER BY hadUserInteraction, isPrevalent, lastSeen LIMIT ?"_s);
2745 if (!recordsToPrune || recordsToPrune->bindInt(1, countLeftToPrune) != SQLITE_OK) {
2746 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::pruneStatisticsIfNeeded failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2747 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2748 return;
2749 }
2750
2751 Vector<unsigned> entriesToPrune;
2752 while (recordsToPrune->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
2753 entriesToPrune.append(recordsToPrune->columnInt(0));
2754
2755 auto listToPrune = buildList(WTF::IteratorRange<Vector<unsigned>::iterator>(entriesToPrune.begin(), entriesToPrune.end()));
2756
2757 auto pruneCommand = m_database.prepareStatementSlow(makeString("DELETE from ObservedDomains WHERE domainID IN (", listToPrune, ")"));
2758 if (!pruneCommand || pruneCommand->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
2759 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::pruneStatisticsIfNeeded failed, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2760 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2761 return;
2762 }
2763}

2874
2875bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::isCorrectSubStatisticsCount(const RegistrableDomain& subframeDomain, const TopFrameDomain& topFrameDomain)
2876{
2877 auto subFrameUnderTopFrameCount = m_database.prepareStatement(countSubframeUnderTopFrameQuery);
2878 auto subresourceUnderTopFrameCount = m_database.prepareStatement(countSubresourceUnderTopFrameQuery);
2879 auto subresourceUniqueRedirectsTo = m_database.prepareStatement(countSubresourceUniqueRedirectsToQuery);
2880
2881 if (!subFrameUnderTopFrameCount || !subresourceUnderTopFrameCount || !subresourceUniqueRedirectsTo) {
2882 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::countSubStatisticsTesting failed to prepare, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2883 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2884 return false;
2885 }
2886
2887 if (subFrameUnderTopFrameCount->bindInt(1, domainID(subframeDomain).value()) != SQLITE_OK
2888 || subFrameUnderTopFrameCount->bindInt(2, domainID(topFrameDomain).value()) != SQLITE_OK
2889 || subresourceUnderTopFrameCount->bindInt(1, domainID(subframeDomain).value()) != SQLITE_OK
2890 || subresourceUnderTopFrameCount->bindInt(2, domainID(topFrameDomain).value()) != SQLITE_OK
2891 || subresourceUniqueRedirectsTo->bindInt(1, domainID(subframeDomain).value()) != SQLITE_OK
2892 || subresourceUniqueRedirectsTo->bindInt(2, domainID(topFrameDomain).value()) != SQLITE_OK) {

2934ASCIILiteral ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::getSubStatisticStatement(const String& tableName) const
2935{
2936 if (tableName == "StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains")
2937 return "SELECT topLevelDomainID from StorageAccessUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE domainID = ?"_s;
2938 if (tableName == "TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo")
2939 return "SELECT toDomainID from TopFrameUniqueRedirectsTo WHERE sourceDomainID = ?"_s;
2940 if (tableName == "TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom")
2941 return "SELECT fromDomainID from TopFrameUniqueRedirectsFrom WHERE targetDomainID = ?"_s;
2942 if (tableName == "TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom")
2943 return "SELECT fromDomainID from TopFrameLinkDecorationsFrom WHERE toDomainID = ?"_s;
2944 if (tableName == "TopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts")
2945 return "SELECT subresourceDomainID from TopFrameLoadedThirdPartyScripts WHERE topFrameDomainID = ?"_s;
2946 if (tableName == "SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains")
2947 return "SELECT topFrameDomainID from SubframeUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE subFrameDomainID = ?"_s;
2948 if (tableName == "SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains")
2949 return "SELECT topFrameDomainID from SubresourceUnderTopFrameDomains WHERE subresourceDomainID = ?"_s;
2950 if (tableName == "SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo")
2951 return "SELECT toDomainID from SubresourceUniqueRedirectsTo WHERE subresourceDomainID = ?"_s;
2952 if (tableName == "SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom")
2953 return "SELECT fromDomainID from SubresourceUniqueRedirectsFrom WHERE subresourceDomainID = ?"_s;
2954
2955 return ""_s;

2958void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::appendSubStatisticList(StringBuilder& builder, const String& tableName, const String& domain) const
2959{
2960 auto query = getSubStatisticStatement(tableName);
2961
2962 if (!query.length())
2963 return;
2964
2965 auto data = m_database.prepareStatement(query);
2966
2967 if (!data || data->bindInt(1, domainID(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromHost(domain)).value()) != SQLITE_OK) {
2968 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::appendSubStatisticList. Statement failed to prepare or bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
2969 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
2970 return;
2971 }
2972
2973 if (data->step() != SQLITE_ROW)
2974 return;
2975
2976 builder.append(" ", tableName, ":\n");
2977
2978 auto result = getDomainStringFromDomainID(data->columnInt(0));
2979 appendNextEntry(builder, result);
2980
2981 while (data->step() == SQLITE_ROW) {
2982 result = getDomainStringFromDomainID(data->columnInt(0));
2983 appendNextEntry(builder, result);
2984 }

3092void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateOperatingDatesParameters()
3093{
3094 auto countOperatingDatesStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM OperatingDates;"_s);
3095 auto getMostRecentOperatingDateStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT * FROM OperatingDates ORDER BY year DESC, month DESC, monthDay DESC LIMIT 1;"_s);
3096 auto getOperatingDateWindowStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT * FROM OperatingDates ORDER BY year DESC, month DESC, monthDay DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET ?;"_s);
3097
3098 if (!countOperatingDatesStatement || countOperatingDatesStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
3099 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateOperatingDatesParameters countOperatingDatesStatement failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3100 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3101 return;
3102 }
3103
3104 m_operatingDatesSize = countOperatingDatesStatement->columnInt(0);
3105
3106 if (!getMostRecentOperatingDateStatement || getMostRecentOperatingDateStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
3107 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateOperatingDatesParameters getFirstOperatingDateStatement failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3108 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3109 return;
3110 }
3111 m_mostRecentOperatingDate = OperatingDate(getMostRecentOperatingDateStatement->columnInt(0), getMostRecentOperatingDateStatement->columnInt(1), getMostRecentOperatingDateStatement->columnInt(2));
3112
3113 if (!getOperatingDateWindowStatement) {
3114 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateOperatingDatesParameters getOperatingDateWindowStatement failed during the call to prepare() with error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING ".", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3115 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3116 return;
3117 }
3118
3119 if (m_operatingDatesSize <= operatingDatesWindowShort - 1)
3120 m_shortWindowOperatingDate = std::nullopt;
3121 else {
3122 if (getOperatingDateWindowStatement->bindInt(1, operatingDatesWindowShort - 1) != SQLITE_OK
3123 || getOperatingDateWindowStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
3124 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateOperatingDatesParameters getOperatingDateWindowStatement failed with error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING ". The error could be in the calls to bind() or step().", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3125 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3126 return;
3127 }
3128 m_shortWindowOperatingDate = OperatingDate(getOperatingDateWindowStatement->columnInt(0), getOperatingDateWindowStatement->columnInt(1), getOperatingDateWindowStatement->columnInt(2));
3129 }
3130
3131 if (m_operatingDatesSize <= operatingDatesWindowLong - 1)
3132 m_longWindowOperatingDate = std::nullopt;
3133 else {
3134 getOperatingDateWindowStatement->reset();
3135 if (getOperatingDateWindowStatement->bindInt(1, operatingDatesWindowLong - 1) != SQLITE_OK
3136 || getOperatingDateWindowStatement->step() != SQLITE_ROW) {
3137 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::updateOperatingDatesParameters getOperatingDateWindowStatement failed with error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING ". The error could be in the calls to bind() or step().", this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3138 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3139 return;
3140 }
3141 m_longWindowOperatingDate = OperatingDate(getOperatingDateWindowStatement->columnInt(0), getOperatingDateWindowStatement->columnInt(1), getOperatingDateWindowStatement->columnInt(2));
3142 }

3145void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::includeTodayAsOperatingDateIfNecessary()
3146{
3147 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
3148
3149 auto today = OperatingDate::today();
3150 if (m_operatingDatesSize > 0) {
3151 if (today <= m_mostRecentOperatingDate)
3152 return;
3153 }
3154
3155 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
3156 transaction.begin();
3157
3158 int rowsToPrune = m_operatingDatesSize - operatingDatesWindowLong + 1;
3159 if (rowsToPrune > 0) {
3160 auto deleteLeastRecentOperatingDateStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("DELETE FROM OperatingDates ORDER BY year, month, monthDay LIMIT ?;"_s);
3161 if (!deleteLeastRecentOperatingDateStatement
3162 || deleteLeastRecentOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(1, rowsToPrune) != SQLITE_OK
3163 || deleteLeastRecentOperatingDateStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
3164 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::includeTodayAsOperatingDateIfNecessary deleteLeastRecentOperatingDateStatement failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3165 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3166 }
3167 }
3168
3169 auto insertOperatingDateStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("INSERT OR IGNORE INTO OperatingDates (year, month, monthDay) SELECT ?, ?, ?;"_s);
3170 if (!insertOperatingDateStatement
3171 || insertOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(1, today.year()) != SQLITE_OK
3172 || insertOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(2, today.month()) != SQLITE_OK
3173 || insertOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(3, today.monthDay()) != SQLITE_OK
3174 || insertOperatingDateStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
3175 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::includeTodayAsOperatingDateIfNecessary insertOperatingDateStatement failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3176 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3177 }
3178
3179 updateOperatingDatesParameters();
3180
3181 transaction.commit();
3182}
3183
3184bool ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::hasStatisticsExpired(WallTime mostRecentUserInteractionTime, OperatingDatesWindow operatingDatesWindow) const
3185{
3186 ASSERT(!RunLoop::isMain());
3187
3188 switch (operatingDatesWindow) {
3189 case OperatingDatesWindow::Long:
3190 if (m_longWindowOperatingDate && OperatingDate::fromWallTime(mostRecentUserInteractionTime) < *m_longWindowOperatingDate)
3191 return true;
3192 break;
3193 case OperatingDatesWindow::Short:
3194 if (m_shortWindowOperatingDate && OperatingDate::fromWallTime(mostRecentUserInteractionTime) < *m_shortWindowOperatingDate)
3195 return true;
3196 break;
3197 case OperatingDatesWindow::ForLiveOnTesting:
3198 return WallTime::now() > mostRecentUserInteractionTime + operatingTimeWindowForLiveOnTesting;
3199 case OperatingDatesWindow::ForReproTesting:
3200 return true;
3201 }
3202
3203 // If we don't meet the real criteria for an expired statistic, check the user setting for a tighter restriction (mainly for testing).
3204 if (this->parameters().timeToLiveUserInteraction) {
3205 if (WallTime::now() > mostRecentUserInteractionTime + this->parameters().timeToLiveUserInteraction.value())
3206 return true;
3207 }
3208 return false;
3209}

3211void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertExpiredStatisticForTesting(const RegistrableDomain& domain, unsigned numberOfOperatingDaysPassed, bool hasUserInteraction, bool isScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval, bool isPrevalent)
3212{
3213 // Populate the Operating Dates table with enough days to require pruning.
3214 double daysAgoInSeconds = 0;
3215
3216 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
3217 transaction.begin();
3218
3219 for (unsigned i = 1; i <= numberOfOperatingDaysPassed; i++) {
3220 double daysToSubtract = Seconds::fromHours(24 * i).value();
3221 daysAgoInSeconds = WallTime::now().secondsSinceEpoch().value() - daysToSubtract;
3222 auto dateToInsert = OperatingDate::fromWallTime(WallTime::fromRawSeconds(daysAgoInSeconds));
3223
3224 auto insertOperatingDateStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("INSERT OR IGNORE INTO OperatingDates (year, month, monthDay) SELECT ?, ?, ?;"_s);
3225 if (!insertOperatingDateStatement
3226 || insertOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(1, dateToInsert.year()) != SQLITE_OK
3227 || insertOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(2, dateToInsert.month()) != SQLITE_OK
3228 || insertOperatingDateStatement->bindInt(3, dateToInsert.monthDay()) != SQLITE_OK
3229 || insertOperatingDateStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
3230 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertExpiredStatisticForTesting insertOperatingDateStatement failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3231 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3232 }
3233 insertOperatingDateStatement->reset();
3234 }
3235
3236 updateOperatingDatesParameters();
3237
3238 transaction.commit();
3239
3240 // Make sure mostRecentUserInteractionTime is the least recent of all entries.
3241 daysAgoInSeconds -= Seconds::fromHours(24).value();
3242 auto scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement = this->scopedStatement(m_insertObservedDomainStatement, insertObservedDomainQuery, "insertExpiredStatisticForTesting"_s);
3243 if (scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindText(RegistrableDomainIndex, domain.string()) != SQLITE_OK
3244 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindDouble(LastSeenIndex, daysAgoInSeconds) != SQLITE_OK
3245 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(HadUserInteractionIndex, hasUserInteraction) != SQLITE_OK
3246 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindDouble(MostRecentUserInteractionTimeIndex, daysAgoInSeconds) != SQLITE_OK
3247 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(GrandfatheredIndex, false) != SQLITE_OK
3248 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(IsPrevalentIndex, isPrevalent) != SQLITE_OK
3249 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(IsVeryPrevalentIndex, false) != SQLITE_OK
3250 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(DataRecordsRemovedIndex, 0) != SQLITE_OK
3251 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(TimesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToUserInteractionIndex, 0) != SQLITE_OK
3252 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(TimesAccessedAsFirstPartyDueToStorageAccessAPIIndex, 0) != SQLITE_OK
3253 || scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->bindInt(IsScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemovalIndex, isScheduledForAllButCookieDataRemoval) != SQLITE_OK) {
3254 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertExpiredStatisticForTesting failed to bind, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3255 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3256 return;
3257 }
3258
3259 if (scopedInsertObservedDomainStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
3260 RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(Network, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertExpiredStatisticForTesting failed to commit, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3261 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3262 return;
3263 }

3265
3266PrivateClickMeasurement ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::buildPrivateClickMeasurementFromDatabase(WebCore::SQLiteStatement* statement, PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType attributionType)
3267{
3268 auto sourceSiteDomain = getDomainStringFromDomainID(statement->columnInt(0));
3269 auto destinationSiteDomain = getDomainStringFromDomainID(statement->columnInt(1));
3270 auto sourceID = statement->columnInt(2);
3271 auto timeOfAdClick = attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed ? statement->columnDouble(5) : statement->columnDouble(3);
3272 auto token = attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed ? statement->columnText(7) : statement->columnText(4);
3273 auto signature = attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed ? statement->columnText(8) : statement->columnText(5);
3274 auto keyID = attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed ? statement->columnText(9) : statement->columnText(6);
3275
3276 PrivateClickMeasurement attribution(WebCore::PrivateClickMeasurement::SourceID(sourceID), WebCore::PrivateClickMeasurement::SourceSite(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(sourceSiteDomain)), WebCore::PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionDestinationSite(RegistrableDomain::uncheckedCreateFromRegistrableDomainString(destinationSiteDomain)), { }, { }, WallTime::fromRawSeconds(timeOfAdClick));
3277
3278 if (attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed) {
3279 auto attributionTriggerData = statement->columnInt(3);
3280 auto priority = statement->columnInt(4);
3281 auto sourceEarliestTimeToSendValue = statement->columnDouble(6);
3282 auto destinationEarliestTimeToSendValue = statement->columnDouble(10);
3283
3284 if (attributionTriggerData != -1)
3285 attribution.setAttribution(WebCore::PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionTriggerData { static_cast<uint32_t>(attributionTriggerData), WebCore::PrivateClickMeasurement::Priority(priority) });
3286
3287 std::optional<WallTime> sourceEarliestTimeToSend;
3288 std::optional<WallTime> destinationEarliestTimeToSend;
3289
3290 // A value of 0.0 indicates that the report has been sent to the respective site.
3291 if (sourceEarliestTimeToSendValue > 0.0)
3292 sourceEarliestTimeToSend = WallTime::fromRawSeconds(sourceEarliestTimeToSendValue);
3293
3294 if (destinationEarliestTimeToSendValue > 0.0)
3295 destinationEarliestTimeToSend = WallTime::fromRawSeconds(destinationEarliestTimeToSendValue);
3296
3297 attribution.setTimesToSend({ sourceEarliestTimeToSend, destinationEarliestTimeToSend });
3298 }
3299
3300 attribution.setSourceSecretToken({ token, signature, keyID });
3301
3302 return attribution;
3303}

3323 || findAttributedScopedStatement->bindInt(1, *sourceSiteDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
3324 || findAttributedScopedStatement->bindInt(2, *destinationSiteDomainID) != SQLITE_OK) {
3325 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::findPrivateClickMeasurement findAttributedQuery, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3326 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();

3328
3329 std::optional<UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement> unattributedPrivateClickMeasurement;
3330 if (findUnattributedScopedStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
3331 unattributedPrivateClickMeasurement = buildPrivateClickMeasurementFromDatabase(findUnattributedScopedStatement.get(), PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Unattributed);
3332
3333 std::optional<AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement> attributedPrivateClickMeasurement;
3334 if (findAttributedScopedStatement->step() == SQLITE_ROW)
3335 attributedPrivateClickMeasurement = buildPrivateClickMeasurementFromDatabase(findAttributedScopedStatement.get(), PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed);
3336
3337 return std::make_pair(unattributedPrivateClickMeasurement, attributedPrivateClickMeasurement);

3340void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertPrivateClickMeasurement(PrivateClickMeasurement&& attribution, PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType attributionType)
3341{
3342 SQLiteTransaction transaction(m_database);
3343 transaction.begin();
3344 auto commitTransaction = makeScopeExit([&transaction] { transaction.commit(); });
3345
3346 auto sourceData = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(attribution.sourceSite().registrableDomain);
3347 auto attributionDestinationData = ensureResourceStatisticsForRegistrableDomain(attribution.destinationSite().registrableDomain);
3348
3349 if (!sourceData.second || !attributionDestinationData.second)
3350 return;
3351
3352 auto& sourceUnlinkableToken = attribution.sourceUnlinkableToken();
3353 if (attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed) {
3354 auto attributionTriggerData = attribution.attributionTriggerData() ? attribution.attributionTriggerData().value().data : -1;
3355 auto priority = attribution.attributionTriggerData() ? attribution.attributionTriggerData().value().priority : -1;
3356 auto sourceEarliestTimeToSend = attribution.timesToSend().sourceEarliestTimeToSend ? attribution.timesToSend().sourceEarliestTimeToSend.value().secondsSinceEpoch().value() : -1;
3357 auto destinationEarliestTimeToSend = attribution.timesToSend().destinationEarliestTimeToSend ? attribution.timesToSend().destinationEarliestTimeToSend.value().secondsSinceEpoch().value() : -1;
3358
3359 // We should never be inserting an attributed private click measurement value into the database without valid report times.
3360 ASSERT(sourceEarliestTimeToSend != -1 && destinationEarliestTimeToSend != -1);
3361
3362 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement(insertAttributedPrivateClickMeasurementQuery);
3363 if (!statement
3364 || statement->bindInt(1, *sourceData.second) != SQLITE_OK
3365 || statement->bindInt(2, *attributionDestinationData.second) != SQLITE_OK
3366 || statement->bindInt(3, attribution.sourceID().id) != SQLITE_OK
3367 || statement->bindInt(4, attributionTriggerData) != SQLITE_OK
3368 || statement->bindInt(5, priority) != SQLITE_OK
3369 || statement->bindDouble(6, attribution.timeOfAdClick().secondsSinceEpoch().value()) != SQLITE_OK
3370 || statement->bindDouble(7, sourceEarliestTimeToSend) != SQLITE_OK
3371 || statement->bindText(8, sourceUnlinkableToken ? sourceUnlinkableToken->tokenBase64URL : emptyString()) != SQLITE_OK
3372 || statement->bindText(9, sourceUnlinkableToken ? sourceUnlinkableToken->signatureBase64URL : emptyString()) != SQLITE_OK
3373 || statement->bindText(10, sourceUnlinkableToken ? sourceUnlinkableToken->keyIDBase64URL : emptyString()) != SQLITE_OK
3374 || statement->bindDouble(11, destinationEarliestTimeToSend) != SQLITE_OK
3375 || statement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
3376 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::insertPrivateClickMeasurement insertAttributedPrivateClickMeasurementQuery, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3377 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3378 }
3379 return;
3380 }
3381
3382 auto statement = m_database.prepareStatement(insertUnattributedPrivateClickMeasurementQuery);
3383 if (!statement
3384 || statement->bindInt(1, *sourceData.second) != SQLITE_OK
3385 || statement->bindInt(2, *attributionDestinationData.second) != SQLITE_OK
3386 || statement->bindInt(3, attribution.sourceID().id) != SQLITE_OK
3387 || statement->bindDouble(4, attribution.timeOfAdClick().secondsSinceEpoch().value()) != SQLITE_OK
3388 || statement->bindText(5, sourceUnlinkableToken ? sourceUnlinkableToken->tokenBase64URL : emptyString()) != SQLITE_OK
3389 || statement->bindText(6, sourceUnlinkableToken ? sourceUnlinkableToken->signatureBase64URL : emptyString()) != SQLITE_OK

3426std::optional<PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionSecondsUntilSendData> ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::attributePrivateClickMeasurement(const SourceSite& sourceSite, const AttributionDestinationSite& destinationSite, AttributionTriggerData&& attributionTriggerData)
3427{
3428 // We should always clear expired clicks from the database before scheduling an attribution.
3429 clearExpiredPrivateClickMeasurement();
3430
3431 if (!attributionTriggerData.isValid()) {
3432 if (UNLIKELY(debugModeEnabled())) {
3433 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(PrivateClickMeasurement, "Got an invalid attribution.");
3434 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::PrivateClickMeasurement, MessageLevel::Error, "[Private Click Measurement] Got an invalid attribution."_s);
3435 }
3436 return std::nullopt;
3437 }
3438
3439 auto data = attributionTriggerData.data;
3440 auto priority = attributionTriggerData.priority;
3441
3442 if (UNLIKELY(debugModeEnabled())) {
3443 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(PrivateClickMeasurement, "Got an attribution with attribution trigger data: %{public}u and priority: %{public}u.", data, priority);
3444 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::PrivateClickMeasurement, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[Private Click Measurement] Got an attribution with attribution trigger data: '"_s, data, "' and priority: '"_s, priority, "'."_s));
3445 }
3446
3447 PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionSecondsUntilSendData secondsUntilSend { std::nullopt, std::nullopt };
3448
3449 auto attribution = findPrivateClickMeasurement(sourceSite, destinationSite);
3450 auto& previouslyUnattributed = attribution.first;
3451 auto& previouslyAttributed = attribution.second;
3452
3453 if (previouslyUnattributed) {
3454 // Always convert the pending attribution and remove it from the unattributed map.
3455 removeUnattributed(*previouslyUnattributed);
3456 secondsUntilSend = previouslyUnattributed.value().attributeAndGetEarliestTimeToSend(WTFMove(attributionTriggerData));
3457
3458 // We should always have a valid secondsUntilSend value for a previouslyUnattributed value because there can be no previous attribution with a higher priority.
3459 if (!secondsUntilSend.hasValidSecondsUntilSendValues()) {
3460 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3461 return std::nullopt;
3462 }
3463
3464 if (UNLIKELY(debugModeEnabled())) {
3465 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(PrivateClickMeasurement, "Converted a stored ad click with attribution trigger data: %{public}u and priority: %{public}u.", data, priority);
3466 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::PrivateClickMeasurement, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[Private Click Measurement] Converted a stored ad click with attribution trigger data: '"_s, data, "' and priority: '"_s, priority, "'."_s));
3467 }
3468
3469 // If there is no previous attribution, or the new attribution has higher priority, insert/update the database.
3470 if (!previouslyAttributed || previouslyUnattributed.value().hasHigherPriorityThan(*previouslyAttributed)) {
3471 insertPrivateClickMeasurement(WTFMove(*previouslyUnattributed), PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed);
3472
3473 if (UNLIKELY(debugModeEnabled())) {
3474 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(PrivateClickMeasurement, "Replaced a previously converted ad click with a new one with attribution data: %{public}u and priority: %{public}u because it had higher priority.", data, priority);
3475 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::PrivateClickMeasurement, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[Private Click Measurement] Replaced a previously converted ad click with a new one with attribution trigger data: '"_s, data, "' and priority: '"_s, priority, "' because it had higher priority."_s));
3476 }
3477 }
3478 } else if (previouslyAttributed) {
3479 // If we have no new attribution, re-attribute the old one to respect the new priority, but only if this report has
3480 // not been sent to the source or destination site yet.
3481 if (!previouslyAttributed.value().hasPreviouslyBeenReported()) {
3482 auto secondsUntilSend = previouslyAttributed.value().attributeAndGetEarliestTimeToSend(WTFMove(attributionTriggerData));
3483 if (!secondsUntilSend.hasValidSecondsUntilSendValues())
3484 return std::nullopt;
3485
3486 insertPrivateClickMeasurement(WTFMove(*previouslyAttributed), PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed);
3487
3488 if (UNLIKELY(debugModeEnabled())) {
3489 RELEASE_LOG_INFO(PrivateClickMeasurement, "Re-converted an ad click with a new one with attribution trigger data: %{public}u and priority: %{public}u because it had higher priority.", data, priority);
3490 debugBroadcastConsoleMessage(MessageSource::PrivateClickMeasurement, MessageLevel::Info, makeString("[Private Click Measurement] Re-converted an ad click with a new one with attribution trigger data: '"_s, data, "' and priority: '"_s, priority, "'' because it had higher priority."_s));
3491 }
3492 }
3493 }
3494
3495 if (!secondsUntilSend.hasValidSecondsUntilSendValues())
3496 return std::nullopt;
3497
3498 return secondsUntilSend;
3499}

3569String ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::attributionToString(WebCore::SQLiteStatement* statement, PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType attributionType)
3570{
3571 auto sourceSiteDomain = getDomainStringFromDomainID(statement->columnInt(0));
3572 auto destinationSiteDomain = getDomainStringFromDomainID(statement->columnInt(1));
3573 auto sourceID = statement->columnInt(2);
3574
3575 StringBuilder builder;
3576 builder.append("Source site: ", sourceSiteDomain, "\nAttribute on site: ", destinationSiteDomain, "\nSource ID: ", sourceID);
3577
3578 if (attributionType == PrivateClickMeasurementAttributionType::Attributed) {
3579 auto attributionTriggerData = statement->columnInt(3);
3580 auto priority = statement->columnInt(4);
3581 auto earliestTimeToSend = statement->columnInt(6);
3582
3583 if (attributionTriggerData != -1) {
3584 builder.append("\nAttribution trigger data: ", attributionTriggerData, "\nAttribution priority: ", priority, "\nAttribution earliest time to send: ");
3585 if (earliestTimeToSend == -1)
3586 builder.append("Not set");
3587 else {
3588 auto secondsUntilSend = WallTime::fromRawSeconds(earliestTimeToSend) - WallTime::now();
3589 builder.append((secondsUntilSend >= 24_h && secondsUntilSend <= 48_h) ? "Within 24-48 hours" : "Outside 24-48 hours");
3590 }
3591 } else
3592 builder.append("\nNo attribution trigger data.");
3593 } else
3594 builder.append("\nNo attribution trigger data.");
3595 builder.append('\n');
3596
3597 return builder.toString();
3598}

3601{
3602 auto privateClickMeasurementDataExists = m_database.prepareStatement("SELECT (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM UnattributedPrivateClickMeasurement) as cnt1, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement) as cnt2"_s);

3701void ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::clearSentAttribution(WebCore::PrivateClickMeasurement&& attribution, PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionReportEndpoint attributionReportEndpoint)
3702{
3703 auto timesToSend = earliestTimesToSend(attribution);
3704 auto sourceEarliestTimeToSend = timesToSend.first;
3705 auto destinationEarliestTimeToSend = timesToSend.second;
3706
3707 auto sourceSiteDomainID = domainID(attribution.sourceSite().registrableDomain);
3708 auto destinationSiteDomainID = domainID(attribution.destinationSite().registrableDomain);
3709
3710 if (!sourceSiteDomainID || !destinationSiteDomainID)
3711 return;
3712
3713 switch (attributionReportEndpoint) {
3714 case PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionReportEndpoint::Source:
3715 if (!sourceEarliestTimeToSend) {
3716 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3717 return;
3718 }
3719 markReportAsSentToSource(*sourceSiteDomainID, *destinationSiteDomainID);
3720 sourceEarliestTimeToSend = std::nullopt;
3721 break;
3722 case PrivateClickMeasurement::AttributionReportEndpoint::Destination:
3723 if (!destinationEarliestTimeToSend) {
3724 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3725 return;
3726 }
3727 markReportAsSentToDestination(*sourceSiteDomainID, *destinationSiteDomainID);
3728 destinationEarliestTimeToSend = std::nullopt;
3729 }
3730
3731 // Don't clear the attribute from the database unless it has been reported both to the source and destination site.
3732 if (destinationEarliestTimeToSend || sourceEarliestTimeToSend)
3733 return;
3734
3735 auto clearAttributedStatement = m_database.prepareStatement("DELETE FROM AttributedPrivateClickMeasurement WHERE sourceSiteDomainID = ? AND destinationSiteDomainID = ?"_s);
3736 if (!clearAttributedStatement
3737 || clearAttributedStatement->bindInt(1, *sourceSiteDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
3738 || clearAttributedStatement->bindInt(2, *destinationSiteDomainID) != SQLITE_OK
3739 || clearAttributedStatement->step() != SQLITE_DONE) {
3740 ITP_RELEASE_LOG_ERROR(m_sessionID, "%p - ResourceLoadStatisticsDatabaseStore::clearSentAttribution failed to step, error message: %" PRIVATE_LOG_STRING, this, m_database.lastErrorMsg());
3741 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
3742 }
3743}
